16:03.833 --> 16:06.791
<i>I want you to put together</i>
<i>a team and get it out.</i>

16:07.375 --> 16:08.416
<i>In exchange,</i>

16:08.916 --> 16:13.041
<i>50 million is yours to divvy up</i>
<i>amongst whomever you take in with you.</i>

16:14.083 --> 16:15.125
<i>Intrigued?</i>

16:16.458 --> 16:17.583
<i>Don't give me an answer.</i>

16:17.666 --> 16:19.166
<i>Think on it for the night.</i>

16:19.250 --> 16:20.625
<i>[cash register beeping]</i>

16:23.333 --> 16:24.458
<i>In good faith.</i>

16:26.791 --> 16:29.125
<i>[Tanaka] We'll talk soon, Mr. Ward.</i>

16:49.416 --> 16:50.375
<i>[sniffs]</i>

16:50.458 --> 16:51.708
<i>[man on TV] </i>You should just be happy

16:51.791 --> 16:54.875
<i>that this is essentially</i>
<i>a government-funded health care solution</i>

16:54.958 --> 16:57.125
<i>that will put an end to all of this.</i>

16:57.208 --> 16:59.583
<i>[woman] </i>Come on, Sean.
You know they're not infected.

16:59.666 --> 17:01.833
<i>If they were,</i>
<i>they would be zombies already.</i>

17:01.916 --> 17:04.166
<i>They're political prisoners,</i>
<i>just</i> <i>people the government</i>

17:04.250 --> 17:05.541
<i>doesn't want on the streets.</i>

17:05.625 --> 17:08.791
<i>You know as well as I do, if you have</i>
<i>questionable immigration status,</i>

17:08.875 --> 17:11.083
<i>advocate for gay rights or abortion,</i>

17:11.166 --> 17:12.541
<i>the next thing you know,</i>

17:12.625 --> 17:14.625
<i>they have a temperature gun at your head</i>

17:14.708 --> 17:16.708
<i>or dragging you out</i>
<i>of your house or your car</i>

17:16.791 --> 17:18.458
<i>under the guise of public safety.</i>

17:18.541 --> 17:21.541
<i>[Sean] </i>We've tested
thousands of nukes in the Nevada desert.

17:21.625 --> 17:23.666
<i>This is no different.</i>

17:24.291 --> 17:25.875
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

17:30.833 --> 17:34.666
<i>[man over PA] </i>Attention detainees
of Las Vegas McCarran quarantine camp.

17:34.750 --> 17:37.666
<i>This facility is in an active evacuation.</i>

17:38.166 --> 17:40.125
<i>Board the shuttle bus for Barstow.</i>

17:40.708 --> 17:43.291
<i>Have your current</i>
<i>temporary health clearance card</i>

17:43.375 --> 17:46.291
<i>to present to officials</i>
<i>as you board the shuttle.</i>

17:46.375 --> 17:48.666
<i>Reminder, shuttles</i>
<i>will be leaving every 15 minutes.</i>

17:48.750 --> 17:50.208
<i>-Hey, guys.</i>
<i>-Kate!</i>

17:50.833 --> 17:52.583
<i>Hi. [gags] I can't breathe.</i>

17:52.666 --> 17:54.750
<i>-You guys excited for the big move?</i>
<i>-Yeah!</i>

17:54.833 --> 17:57.375
<i>Kate, let the kids finish packing.</i>

17:57.458 --> 17:58.583
<i>Go on. Come on.</i>

18:00.750 --> 18:03.250
<i>Kate, I need you to promise me something.</i>

18:03.333 --> 18:06.375
<i>In case anything</i>
<i>happens to me in the next few days,</i>

18:06.458 --> 18:09.083
<i>just make sure</i>
<i>the kids make it out to Barstow. Okay?</i>

18:09.708 --> 18:11.958
<i>What do you mean? What could happen?</i>

18:12.041 --> 18:12.875
<i>[sighs]</i>

18:15.125 --> 18:16.375
<i>You know her, don't you?</i>

18:18.833 --> 18:20.041
<i>The coyote.</i>

18:20.666 --> 18:23.583
<i>Geeta, that is not an option.</i>

18:23.666 --> 18:26.250
<i>[whispering] Kate,</i>
<i>she helps people get in,</i>

18:26.333 --> 18:28.250
<i>crack a slot machine, slip back out.</i>

18:28.333 --> 18:30.250
<i>Before anyone even knows, you're gone.</i>

18:31.416 --> 18:33.458
<i>That money is our ticket out of here,</i>

18:33.541 --> 18:35.500
<i>or we'll be trapped in Barstow forever.</i>

18:36.083 --> 18:38.916
<i>Listen, these guards,</i>
<i>they don't give a shit.</i>

18:39.000 --> 18:43.041
<i>But for five grand,</i>
<i>I can buy my way out, me and my kids.</i>

18:44.250 --> 18:47.583
<i>I have to get the kids out by Friday,</i>

18:48.208 --> 18:51.750
<i>and I will do</i>
<i>whatever it takes to protect my family.</i>

18:51.833 --> 18:54.416
<i>Geeta, people that go in there,</i>

18:54.500 --> 18:56.041
<i>they don't always come back.</i>

18:56.125 --> 18:57.208
<i>Just forget it.</i>

18:57.291 --> 19:00.208
<i>-Hey, wait, wait, wait, Geeta, come on.</i>
<i>-Just let it go, okay?</i>

19:00.291 --> 19:01.333
<i>-Well…</i>
<i>-[guard] Hey.</i>

19:03.208 --> 19:04.791
<i>Everything okay here, ladies?</i>

19:06.541 --> 19:08.750
<i>What, you don't have</i>
<i>anything better to do?</i>

19:08.833 --> 19:09.708
<i>Kate…</i>

19:09.791 --> 19:12.791
<i>-The fuck you say to me, volunteer?</i>
<i>-She didn't say anything.</i>

19:12.875 --> 19:15.000
<i>-Is that right, volunteer?</i>
<i>-[Geeta] Kate.</i>

19:15.083 --> 19:18.875
<i>Shut the fuck up! Shut the fuck up!</i>

19:18.958 --> 19:19.791
<i>Okay.</i>

19:20.333 --> 19:22.875
<i>What? Were you saying something to me?</i>

19:23.375 --> 19:24.291
<i>[mouthing] Don't.</i>

19:25.916 --> 19:27.666
<i>No, I didn't say anything.</i>

19:32.208 --> 19:35.541
<i>You know, the first sign</i>
<i>of infection is belligerence</i>

19:36.041 --> 19:38.416
<i>and actions outside of social norms.</i>

19:42.708 --> 19:43.916
<i>[sighs]</i>

19:45.458 --> 19:48.000
<i>Look at me and hold still.</i>

19:51.250 --> 19:52.625
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

19:54.083 --> 19:55.083
<i>[beeping]</i>

19:58.208 --> 19:59.041
<i>Clear.</i>

19:59.125 --> 20:01.041
<i>[woman over PA] </i>Volunteers
and temporary workers,

20:01.125 --> 20:03.500
<i>e</i>mployee shuttles leave in five minutes.

20:04.166 --> 20:05.333
<i>Your turn.</i>

20:06.750 --> 20:07.791
<i>If you want,</i>

20:09.125 --> 20:10.958
<i>I could use my rectal thermometer.</i>

20:15.583 --> 20:17.375
<i>[laughs]</i>

20:22.916 --> 20:24.875
<i>-[beeping]</i>
<i>-[guard] Oh.</i>

20:26.166 --> 20:28.125
<i>You're down a couple of decimal points.</i>

20:28.708 --> 20:30.333
<i>You sure you're feeling all right?</i>

20:30.916 --> 20:33.625
<i>-You sure you're not infected?</i>
<i>-I… I'm fine.</i>

20:33.708 --> 20:36.708
<i>I'm fine. I'm… I feel fine.</i>

20:39.875 --> 20:40.791
<i>Well,</i>

20:42.166 --> 20:45.125
<i>you're both within</i>
<i>the margin of error, but watch it.</i>

20:48.083 --> 20:50.291
<i>You better be on that bus, volunteer.</i>

20:53.250 --> 20:54.125
<i>Asshole.</i>

20:55.166 --> 20:56.625
<i>What were you thinking?</i>

20:56.708 --> 20:59.833
<i>Do you know how easy it would be</i>
<i>for him to make you disappear?</i>

20:59.916 --> 21:02.500
<i>All he has to say</i>
<i>is that you dropped a degree,</i>

21:02.583 --> 21:04.833
<i>and nobody would question it, nobody.</i>

21:05.458 --> 21:06.708
<i>-I know, I'm…</i>
<i>-You know?</i>

21:06.791 --> 21:08.583
<i>I just… He…</i>

21:10.333 --> 21:11.541
<i>Look, it doesn't matter.</i>

21:11.625 --> 21:13.125
<i>-I'm sorry. I just…</i>
<i>-[sniffles]</i>

21:13.750 --> 21:17.791
<i>I need you to promise me</i>
<i>that you're not gonna do anything stupid.</i>

21:18.500 --> 21:21.833
<i>Geeta, it's… it's not worth the risk.</i>

21:23.041 --> 21:24.375
<i>No, you're right.</i>

21:25.166 --> 21:26.125
<i>I won't.</i>

21:27.083 --> 21:28.500
<i>I promise. Okay?</i>

21:29.791 --> 21:30.750
<i>Thanks.</i>

21:30.833 --> 21:33.416
<i>[woman] …</i>employee shuttles
leave in five minutes.

21:40.208 --> 21:43.166
<i>[banging]</i>

21:48.666 --> 21:50.583
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

21:56.083 --> 21:58.000
<i>[growling]</i>

22:14.583 --> 22:16.291
<i>[roaring]</i>

22:56.166 --> 22:57.750
<i>[screaming]</i>

23:13.000 --> 23:15.208
<i>Mom! [wailing]</i>

23:15.291 --> 23:16.875
<i>[gasping and breathing heavily]</i>

23:52.083 --> 23:53.000
<i>[ringing]</i>

23:59.750 --> 24:00.583
<i>Yes?</i>

24:01.333 --> 24:04.000
<i>[Scott] </i>Mr. Tanaka, I'm in a tough spot.

24:05.125 --> 24:06.583
<i>I don't like you very much.</i>

24:08.291 --> 24:11.333
<i>So I hate giving you</i>
<i>the satisfaction of taking the job, but…</i>

24:12.375 --> 24:14.125
<i>[Tanaka] </i>You'd best to gather your team.

24:14.708 --> 24:17.541
<i>You'll need</i>
<i>a helicopter pilot and a safecracker.</i>

24:18.208 --> 24:20.333
<i>I'm gonna text you an address.</i>

24:20.416 --> 24:22.375
<i>Be there at 4:00 p.m. tomorrow.</i>

24:25.000 --> 24:25.875
<i>[phone beeps off]</i>

24:28.708 --> 24:29.750
<i>He's in.</i>

24:30.916 --> 24:33.375
<i>[woman in Spanish] </i>I hate to ask, but…

24:33.458 --> 24:36.625
<i>I have to take the kids to school,</i>
<i>and if I can't get to my job--</i>

24:36.708 --> 24:38.291
<i>Don't worry, I'll fix it.</i>

24:38.375 --> 24:40.166
<i>[sighs in relief] Thank you, Maria.</i>

24:40.250 --> 24:43.083
<i>Don't worry about it.</i>
<i>Careful, I'm all greasy.</i>

24:43.166 --> 24:46.041
<i>-Sharkey, give her the white loaner.</i>
<i>-[Sharkey speaks Spanish]</i>

24:46.125 --> 24:48.500
<i>-Gracias,</i> Maria.
-Say hi to the kids.

24:48.583 --> 24:50.125
<i>[woman in English] Okay. Bye.</i>

24:53.333 --> 24:54.250
<i>Fuck.</i>

24:55.333 --> 24:56.166
<i>[sighs]</i>

25:00.208 --> 25:01.083
<i>Hey.</i>

25:03.875 --> 25:05.875
<i>[chuckling] Hey!</i>

25:07.958 --> 25:09.500
<i>[Scott] So you think it's a bad idea?</i>

25:09.583 --> 25:10.500
<i>[Maria] Come on, Scotty.</i>

25:10.583 --> 25:13.250
<i>It's not a matter of "think."</i>
<i>It's a matter of "is,"</i>

25:13.333 --> 25:17.166
<i>and it is a bad goddamn idea.</i>

25:18.958 --> 25:20.833
<i>-[Scott] You're out?</i>
<i>-I didn't say that.</i>

25:20.916 --> 25:21.791
<i>[Scott] You're in?</i>

25:22.375 --> 25:23.708
<i>I didn't say that either.</i>

25:24.958 --> 25:26.166
<i>But you're intrigued.</i>

25:26.875 --> 25:30.500
<i>That much I'm guessing</i>
<i>your ass knew before you even walked in.</i>

25:31.875 --> 25:33.083
<i>[Scott] I mean, think about it.</i>

25:33.666 --> 25:36.208
<i>Everything we did,</i>
<i>all those people we saved,</i>

25:36.833 --> 25:38.208
<i>look what it got us.</i>

25:38.791 --> 25:41.208
<i>But what if… what if just once,</i>

25:42.250 --> 25:44.083
<i>we did something just for us?</i>

25:49.000 --> 25:50.083
<i>We could die.</i>

25:54.958 --> 25:56.375
<i>Yeah, we'll probably die.</i>

25:56.458 --> 25:57.458
<i>-Hmm.</i>
<i>-[chuckles]</i>

25:58.625 --> 26:00.000
<i>Some of us at least.</i>

26:01.958 --> 26:03.416
<i>Fifty million dollars.</i>

26:04.083 --> 26:05.125
<i>Fifty million.</i>

26:05.208 --> 26:08.166
<i>What's the split? Even however many ways?</i>

26:08.250 --> 26:12.166
<i>Figured you, me, and Vanderohe will take</i>
<i>15 million each, assuming he'll do it.</i>

26:14.791 --> 26:16.458
<i>Everybody else who isn't family…</i>

26:17.333 --> 26:18.916
<i>Nobody needs to know our cut.</i>

26:20.208 --> 26:22.916
<i>Now you're getting it. [chuckling]</i>

26:24.208 --> 26:27.833
<i>[chuckles] Who else</i>
<i>is on your crazy-ass list?</i>

26:27.916 --> 26:29.041
<i>[chuckling]</i>

26:29.833 --> 26:31.125
<i>[bottles clink]</i>

26:32.625 --> 26:34.625
<i>[Vanderohe] So I see you had a visitor.</i>

26:36.208 --> 26:37.708
<i>Talk to me. How'd it go?</i>

26:38.333 --> 26:41.500
<i>[woman] Well, first time she's come</i>
<i>to visit me in six months.</i>

26:41.583 --> 26:44.666
<i>We can't make small talk</i>
<i>for more than 35 minutes</i>

26:44.750 --> 26:46.791
<i>without it turning into a fight.</i>

26:48.166 --> 26:50.041
<i>Still, she seems happy.</i>

26:50.125 --> 26:52.333
<i>That's what matters, I suppose.</i>

26:52.416 --> 26:56.291
<i>I'm sure that she appreciates you,</i>
<i>even if you don't realize it.</i>

26:56.375 --> 26:57.541
<i>-Mmm.</i>
<i>-I mean it.</i>

26:57.625 --> 26:59.916
<i>And if she doesn't… [whispers] …screw her.</i>

27:00.000 --> 27:00.916
<i>[both laugh]</i>

27:02.791 --> 27:04.708
<i>[Vanderohe] That's, uh, some heavy shit.</i>

27:05.208 --> 27:06.458
<i>[Scott] So where's your head at?</i>

27:08.000 --> 27:11.750
<i>You know, when we were in it,</i>
<i>like, when we were really in it,</i>

27:11.833 --> 27:15.791
<i>I never thought about the faces</i>
<i>of all the countless monsters</i>

27:15.875 --> 27:17.875
<i>but now just realized, you know,</i>

27:17.958 --> 27:19.250
<i>were people.</i>

27:19.333 --> 27:20.458
<i>But now their faces,</i>

27:21.125 --> 27:22.250
<i>that's all I see.</i>

27:23.083 --> 27:25.166
<i>I don't know if being back in</i>
<i>would be better or worse.</i>

27:25.250 --> 27:27.583
<i>God, I can't figure that out,</i>

27:27.666 --> 27:30.041
<i>but I guess</i>
<i>there is a chance that it could be…</i>

27:32.041 --> 27:33.166
<i>cathartic.</i>

27:36.375 --> 27:37.291
<i>There it is.</i>

27:38.208 --> 27:39.875
<i>[helicopter blades whirring]</i>

27:40.750 --> 27:42.208
<i>[Peters] Would you look at that.</i>

27:42.791 --> 27:45.500
<i>They should have</i>
<i>nuked Vegas in the early '90s, but…</i>

27:46.208 --> 27:48.500
<i>-This is great.</i>
<i>-[Scott] Peters!</i>

27:50.083 --> 27:52.583
<i>Holy shit.</i>

27:53.208 --> 27:54.208
<i>[Scott] What's up?</i>

27:54.708 --> 27:57.000
<i>-What the hell brings you here?</i>
<i>-[Scott chuckles]</i>

27:57.083 --> 27:57.916
<i>How's the job?</i>

27:58.000 --> 28:00.791
<i>Sucks ass. What're you guys doing here?</i>

28:01.750 --> 28:04.458
<i>-Well--</i>
<i>-We are putting together a crew for a job.</i>

28:04.541 --> 28:05.791
<i>Yeah? What does it pay?</i>

28:05.875 --> 28:07.750
<i>Well, if it pans out,</i>

28:08.583 --> 28:10.541
<i>you make two million dollars</i>
<i>for one day's work.</i>

28:10.625 --> 28:12.208
<i>-Two million dollars?</i>
<i>-But--</i>

28:12.291 --> 28:13.916
<i>[Peters] That's my share. Just for me?</i>

28:14.625 --> 28:17.041
<i>Two million dollars if it pans out?</i>

28:18.875 --> 28:21.041
<i>Hundred percent. I'm in. Yeah.</i>

28:21.125 --> 28:23.416
<i>You don't want to know the risks or--</i>

28:23.500 --> 28:27.416
<i>Why would I want to know the risks?</i>
<i>Two million dollars? That's a lot of cash.</i>

28:27.500 --> 28:31.166
<i>Listen, I hate my life so deeply,</i>

28:31.750 --> 28:33.833
<i>if I had two million dollars,</i>

28:33.916 --> 28:35.625
<i>my life would change drastically.</i>

28:36.166 --> 28:39.083
<i>Yeah. Thank you. Yes.</i>

28:39.166 --> 28:40.625
<i>You sure you don't want to know?</i>

28:40.708 --> 28:41.708
<i>Uh…</i>

28:41.791 --> 28:43.958
<i>I bet it has something</i>
<i>to do with a helicopter.</i>

28:44.041 --> 28:44.875
<i>[Scott] Yeah.</i>

28:44.958 --> 28:46.916
<i>-I'm the helicopter guy. Yeah.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

28:47.541 --> 28:49.541
<i>-Where do I sign?</i>
<i>-[Scott] Okay.</i>

28:49.625 --> 28:51.791
<i>-I'm in.</i>
<i>-[Scott] Thanks. Nice seeing you, bud.</i>

28:52.583 --> 28:54.041
<i>She hasn't changed, has she?</i>

28:54.125 --> 28:56.750
<i>Nope. Still weird as ever.</i>

28:56.833 --> 28:58.666
<i>Come on. This next one's on me.</i>

28:58.750 --> 29:01.791
<i>["Si Señor" by Control Machete playing]</i>

29:01.875 --> 29:03.125
<i>[indistinct chattering]</i>

29:05.208 --> 29:06.458
<i>Come on. Shit.</i>

29:06.541 --> 29:09.791
<i>That's it, baby.</i>
<i>That's what I'm fuckin' talking about!</i>

29:10.625 --> 29:11.833
<i>Mikey Guzman.</i>

29:11.916 --> 29:15.416
<i>-Mikey Guzman. Name rings a bell.</i>
<i>-Mm-hmm.</i>

29:15.500 --> 29:16.500
<i>Check this out.</i>

29:18.083 --> 29:21.083
<i>This is your boy, Mikey Guzman,</i>
<i>taping live from East Las Vegas.</i>

29:21.166 --> 29:22.000
<i>We got a group of…</i>

29:22.083 --> 29:25.208
<i>I counted at least five,</i>
<i>but let me double-check. Hold on.</i>

29:25.291 --> 29:27.208
<i>Seven. We got seven shamblers.</i>

29:27.291 --> 29:28.333
<i>[gunshot]</i>

29:28.416 --> 29:30.958
<i>Boom, motherfucker! Double headshot.</i>

29:33.083 --> 29:34.458
<i>-[gunshot]</i>
<i>-[whooping]</i>

29:35.375 --> 29:36.625
<i>-Shit!</i>
-[Scott] Kid's crazy.

29:36.708 --> 29:39.250
<i>There are Reddit forums</i>
<i>devoted to this guy.</i>

29:40.583 --> 29:41.583
<i>Swagger, baby!</i>

29:42.166 --> 29:44.833
<i>-Swagger, man. Hell, yeah.</i>
<i>-That's how it's done.</i>

29:44.916 --> 29:46.250
<i>Thank you very much.</i>

29:46.333 --> 29:48.416
<i>@GuzmanOfTheDead420.</i>

29:48.500 --> 29:50.166
<i>Make sure to like and subscribe.</i>

29:50.250 --> 29:52.833
<i>Yo, that motherfucker has a Rolex.</i>
<i>That's ten grand at least.</i>

29:52.916 --> 29:53.750
<i>[Guzman] Hey!</i>

29:53.833 --> 29:54.958
<i>Qué onda, güero?</i>

29:55.541 --> 29:56.625
<i>[Scott] Mikey Guzman.</i>

29:57.708 --> 29:58.875
<i>Yo, what's up?</i>

29:58.958 --> 30:01.166
<i>What would you say about making 500 grand?</i>

30:03.541 --> 30:05.583
<i>I'd say, "Who the hell do I gotta kill?"</i>

30:07.333 --> 30:08.375
<i>I love him.</i>

30:11.875 --> 30:13.208
<i>What are we doing here?</i>

30:13.291 --> 30:16.250
<i>You told me you needed a safecracker.</i>
<i>Might be your missing piece.</i>

30:16.875 --> 30:21.125
<i>[Scott] How would you like to make</i>
<i>250 grand for one day's work?</i>

30:22.375 --> 30:23.375
<i>Oh, my God.</i>

30:26.083 --> 30:27.083
<i>[Scott] Can you crack it?</i>

30:27.791 --> 30:29.166
<i>-Can I crack it?</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

30:29.666 --> 30:31.041
<i>[chuckles]</i>

30:32.125 --> 30:33.000
<i>Can I crack it?</i>

30:33.833 --> 30:37.458
<i>This is like showing me a picture</i>
<i>of Botticelli's </i>Madonna of the Magnificat

30:37.541 --> 30:39.416
<i>and asking me if I want to fuck her.</i>

30:40.958 --> 30:45.625
<i>Okay, the man who designed</i>
<i>this wonderful work of art,</i>

30:45.708 --> 30:46.958
<i>Hans Wagner,</i>

30:47.041 --> 30:49.458
<i>he named it </i>Der Götterdämmerung

30:49.541 --> 30:51.708
<i>for the final chapter in his namesake,</i>

30:51.791 --> 30:53.708
<i>Richard Wagner's epic opera,</i>

30:54.541 --> 30:55.958
<i>Der Ring des Nibelungen.</i>

30:56.041 --> 30:58.416
<i>-Mmm.</i>
<i>-[safecracker] Can it be opened and by me?</i>

30:59.083 --> 30:59.916
<i>I don't know.</i>

31:00.000 --> 31:01.458
<i>-I honestly don't.</i>
<i>-Okay.</i>

31:01.541 --> 31:04.250
<i>Watch your fingers, Mr. Big Hand.</i>

31:04.333 --> 31:06.333
<i>But of the world's living locksmiths,</i>

31:06.958 --> 31:09.833
<i>do I represent</i>
<i>your greatest chance of opening it?</i>

31:09.916 --> 31:12.916
<i>I can, with humility, say yes.</i>

31:13.875 --> 31:14.875
<i>You're in?</i>

31:14.958 --> 31:16.833
<i>It's a doorway</i>
<i>to another realm, my friends,</i>

31:17.458 --> 31:19.625
<i>and providence has brought you to me.</i>

31:19.708 --> 31:21.208
<i>We go through it together.</i>

31:21.291 --> 31:23.916
<i>-By the way, what's your name?</i>
<i>-Scott Ward.</i>

31:24.000 --> 31:25.291
<i>-[safecracker] Sorry?</i>
<i>-Scott Ward.</i>

31:25.375 --> 31:27.541
<i>Dieter, Scott Ward.</i>

31:27.625 --> 31:30.250
<i>["Bad Moon Rising"</i>
<i>by Thea Gilmore playing]</i>

31:34.250 --> 31:37.916
<i>♪ I see a bad moon rising ♪</i>

31:40.708 --> 31:44.375
<i>♪ I see trouble on the way ♪</i>

31:47.000 --> 31:51.208
<i>♪ I see earthquakes and lightnin' ♪</i>

31:52.500 --> 31:53.333
<i>[groaning]</i>

31:53.416 --> 31:56.791
<i>♪ I see bad times today ♪</i>

31:59.416 --> 32:02.041
<i>♪ Don't go around tonight ♪</i>

32:02.125 --> 32:05.375
<i>♪ 'Cause it's bound to take your life ♪</i>

32:07.041 --> 32:10.333
<i>♪ There's a bad moon on the rise ♪</i>

32:12.708 --> 32:16.416
<i>♪ I hear hurricanes a-blowing ♪</i>

32:16.500 --> 32:17.625
<i>Are you ready to play?</i>

32:18.916 --> 32:22.375
<i>♪ I know the end is comin' soon ♪</i>

32:25.500 --> 32:29.875
<i>♪ I fear rivers overflowin' ♪</i>

32:31.791 --> 32:36.916
<i>♪ I hear the voice of rage and ruin ♪</i>

32:37.875 --> 32:40.291
<i>♪ Don't go around tonight ♪</i>

32:40.375 --> 32:43.500
<i>♪ 'Cause it's bound to take your life ♪</i>

32:45.416 --> 32:48.916
<i>♪ There's a bad moon on the rise ♪</i>

32:52.541 --> 32:53.625
<i>Yeah.</i>

33:03.916 --> 33:07.416
<i>Scott, this is Damon. That's Chambers.</i>

33:07.500 --> 33:10.041
<i>-They're with me. They'll be on my dime.</i>
<i>-Okay.</i>

33:10.791 --> 33:12.750
<i>-[Damon] How's it going?</i>
<i>-Welcome to the team.</i>

33:12.833 --> 33:15.291
<i>[Vanderohe] Scott, you want to tell me</i>
<i>what's up with the kid?</i>

33:15.375 --> 33:16.500
<i>Look at him. No offense,</i>

33:16.583 --> 33:19.041
<i>but he doesn't look</i>
<i>like zombie killer material.</i>

33:20.125 --> 33:24.416
<i>Hi, my name is Dieter, and I'm going</i>
<i>to open what cannot be opened.</i>

33:24.500 --> 33:25.666
<i>[laughs] Are you kidding me?</i>

33:25.750 --> 33:28.000
<i>[Scott] No, we need the kid</i>
<i>to open the safe.</i>

33:28.791 --> 33:30.250
<i>We lose him, we got nothing.</i>

33:30.333 --> 33:31.916
<i>[clapping slowly]</i>

33:32.000 --> 33:33.416
<i>Let's go, guys. Bring it in.</i>

33:34.000 --> 33:35.791
<i>Mr. Tanaka, team's all here.</i>

33:35.875 --> 33:38.583
<i>[Tanaka] Lovely to have you</i>
<i>all gathered here today.</i>

33:38.666 --> 33:40.000
<i>Meet your target.</i>

33:42.583 --> 33:43.916
<i>The Vegas Bly.</i>

33:44.666 --> 33:46.333
<i>You can't fly into Vegas.</i>

33:47.000 --> 33:48.708
<i>It's restricted airspace.</i>

33:49.208 --> 33:50.458
<i>But you can fly out.</i>

33:51.333 --> 33:56.916
<i>There is an abandoned rescue helicopter</i>
<i>on top of the north tower, Sodom.</i>

33:57.500 --> 34:00.333
<i>If you coordinate and communicate,</i>

34:00.416 --> 34:02.625
<i>this should be a simple in-and-out.</i>

34:03.208 --> 34:04.333
<i>[techno music playing]</i>

34:05.333 --> 34:09.125
<i>[Tanaka] </i>You will enter the city
with a 32-hour window.

34:09.208 --> 34:11.125
<i>Whatever zombies are still walking</i>

34:11.208 --> 34:15.333
<i>should be no problem for a gang</i>
<i>of tough </i>hombres<i> such as yourselves.</i>

34:37.833 --> 34:39.833
<i>Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait, wait!</i>

34:39.916 --> 34:41.500
<i>[music slows to a halt]</i>

34:42.666 --> 34:43.791
<i>My apologies.</i>

34:43.875 --> 34:46.291
<i>How precisely do we do the zombie killing?</i>

34:46.958 --> 34:48.250
<i>Oh, Jesus.</i>

34:48.916 --> 34:49.750
<i>[laughing]</i>

34:49.833 --> 34:52.916
<i>[Scott] Is there anybody else here</i>
<i>who hasn't killed a zombie?</i>

34:54.125 --> 34:55.166
<i>[scoffs]</i>

34:55.250 --> 34:57.583
<i>Well, we all know the basics.</i>

34:57.666 --> 35:00.416
<i>Zombies, shamblers, the undead,</i>
<i>whatever you wanna call them,</i>

35:00.500 --> 35:03.041
<i>when it comes to killing them,</i>
<i>it's all about the brain.</i>

35:03.125 --> 35:03.958
<i>Brain.</i>

35:04.041 --> 35:07.833
<i>One comes at you, shoot it in the brain.</i>
<i>It's that simple. Any questions?</i>

35:09.000 --> 35:13.541
<i>Yes. What if I took a big rock</i>
<i>and smashed it into the head?</i>

35:13.625 --> 35:14.833
<i>Would… would that work?</i>

35:16.166 --> 35:18.166
<i>Yeah. Yeah, that, uh…</i>

35:18.250 --> 35:21.000
<i>that also would still be targeting</i>
<i>the brain, so that would work.</i>

35:21.083 --> 35:22.125
<i>Copy that.</i>

35:22.208 --> 35:24.125
<i>Sorry, Mr. Tanaka, please continue.</i>

35:25.208 --> 35:27.166
<i>[techno music continues playing]</i>

35:27.250 --> 35:29.875
<i>[Tanaka] </i>From there,
you move down the Strip.

35:33.250 --> 35:35.958
<i>You'll reach the casino</i>
<i>in less than two hours.</i>

35:36.541 --> 35:38.625
<i>You go in and find the generator.</i>

35:41.416 --> 35:44.375
<i>The safe,</i>
<i>beneath the south tower, Gomorrah…</i>

35:46.375 --> 35:48.500
<i>is at the end of a hallway.</i>

35:48.583 --> 35:51.583
<i>There, you'll find</i>
<i>several nonlethal deterrents.</i>

35:51.666 --> 35:53.875
<i>You'll have to find a way to trigger them.</i>

35:54.541 --> 35:58.041
<i>Meanwhile,</i>
<i>our fearless pilot-slash-mechanic</i>

35:58.125 --> 35:59.208
<i>fuels the helicopter.</i>

36:04.083 --> 36:05.833
<i>Back at the main door,</i>

36:05.916 --> 36:08.166
<i>our safecracker gets to work.</i>

36:09.791 --> 36:12.875
<i>Like a surgeon or a painter,</i>

36:13.458 --> 36:17.541
<i>his masterpiece rendered</i>
<i>in barely audible clicks.</i>

36:18.750 --> 36:20.958
<i>Finally, she succumbs</i>
<i>to the sheer dominance</i>

36:21.041 --> 36:23.083
<i>of his gentle touch.</i>

36:26.041 --> 36:30.333
<i>Then, all you have to do</i>
<i>is load the money on the helicopter</i>

36:30.416 --> 36:33.541
<i>and fly off into the sunset.</i>

36:38.041 --> 36:39.666
<i>-All this…</i>
<i>-[snaps fingers]</i>

36:39.750 --> 36:42.458
<i>…a full day before the nuke</i>
<i>ever leaves the launchpad.</i>

36:42.541 --> 36:45.041
<i>Easy peasy Japanese-y.</i>

36:46.083 --> 36:47.458
<i>[clears throat] Sorry, sir.</i>

36:47.541 --> 36:51.083
<i>We're not allowed to say that anymore.</i>
<i>It's "lemon squeezy" now.</i>

36:52.041 --> 36:53.541
<i>Yeah, but I'm--</i>

36:53.625 --> 36:55.541
<i>I think it's fine if he's Japanese-y.</i>

36:56.875 --> 36:57.958
<i>[Tanaka] As you wish.</i>

36:58.041 --> 37:01.375
<i>Easy peasy lemon squeezy.</i>

37:02.750 --> 37:03.708
<i>Take a look.</i>

37:06.875 --> 37:08.041
<i>[sighs in exasperation]</i>

37:09.875 --> 37:12.208
<i>Oh. Okay. Good job. Good job.</i>

37:16.791 --> 37:21.500
<i>Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait. Hold on.</i>
<i>This is the real plan? It's zombies?</i>

37:21.583 --> 37:24.958
<i>Yeah, bro, what's going on?</i>
<i>I thought you were cool with it.</i>

37:25.625 --> 37:28.916
<i>You were always talking about how, if you</i>
<i>saw a zombie, you'd fuck his shit up.</i>

37:29.000 --> 37:30.791
<i>That was bullshit, man.</i>

37:30.875 --> 37:31.708
<i>What?</i>

37:31.791 --> 37:33.416
<i>[Damon] Fuck this. I'm out.</i>

37:33.500 --> 37:35.875
<i>This is crazy. You all are gonna die.</i>

37:35.958 --> 37:37.500
<i>-Jesus Christ.</i>
<i>-[Damon] Sorry, brother.</i>

37:37.583 --> 37:39.250
<i>[Scott] Amateurs.</i>

37:39.333 --> 37:42.125
<i>Hey, Damon. Wait, man.</i>

37:42.208 --> 37:44.458
<i>[Scott] All right, team,</i>
<i>grab your load-out bags.</i>

37:44.541 --> 37:45.750
<i>See you at 6:00 a.m. sharp.</i>

37:45.833 --> 37:47.333
<i>[Vanderohe] Roger that, Cap.</i>

37:47.916 --> 37:49.500
<i>Now, hold up, hold up.</i>

37:50.208 --> 37:52.750
<i>My name's Martin.</i>
<i>I'm Mr. Tanaka's head of security.</i>

37:54.041 --> 37:56.125
<i>Anything you need, you talk to me.</i>

37:57.083 --> 37:59.250
<i>I can access any hardware you might want.</i>

37:59.333 --> 38:01.125
<i>I'll also be accompanying you on this job</i>

38:01.208 --> 38:03.625
<i>because of my</i>
<i>extensive knowledge of the casino.</i>

38:04.250 --> 38:05.083
<i>Any questions?</i>

38:06.333 --> 38:08.208
<i>Good. See you at 0600.</i>

38:09.208 --> 38:10.375
<i>[Dieter] 0600?</i>

38:10.458 --> 38:11.791
<i>[Tanaka] How're you feeling?</i>

38:11.875 --> 38:13.500
<i>[Scott] You're insane.</i>
<i>You know that, right?</i>

38:13.583 --> 38:15.500
<i>But if it's a choice</i>
<i>between dying on the Strip</i>

38:15.583 --> 38:18.583
<i>and spending another day</i>
<i>flipping patties at the Lucky Boy,</i>

38:19.583 --> 38:21.166
<i>I'll gamble on a few million.</i>

38:21.250 --> 38:24.708
<i>Have you given</i>
<i>any thought to how you'll get in?</i>

38:26.083 --> 38:26.916
<i>Yeah.</i>

38:27.000 --> 38:30.250
<i>[woman over PA] </i>Recent arrivals
require a full health inspection.

38:30.333 --> 38:34.333
<i>Barstow Quarantine Center</i>
<i>is a zero-tolerance facility.</i>

38:35.000 --> 38:38.125
<i>Without a green health clearance sticker</i>
<i>on your key card,</i>

38:38.208 --> 38:40.583
<i>you will not be permitted in common areas.</i>

38:41.833 --> 38:43.416
<i>[Scott] Hey. Kate.</i>

38:45.750 --> 38:48.416
<i>-What are you doing here?</i>
<i>-I need to talk to you.</i>

38:48.500 --> 38:49.625
<i>-No. No!</i>
<i>-Wait. Whoa!</i>

38:49.708 --> 38:52.000
<i>Just hear me out. Hear me out.</i>

38:52.750 --> 38:54.541
<i>[man speaking Spanish over PA]</i>

38:55.875 --> 38:57.250
<i>I have an opportunity,</i>

38:58.916 --> 38:59.875
<i>and I need your help.</i>

38:59.958 --> 39:01.166
<i>[laughs sarcastically]</i>

39:01.916 --> 39:04.583
<i>Look. I know this is gonna sound crazy.</i>

39:04.666 --> 39:06.375
<i>But do one thing for me.</i>

39:06.458 --> 39:07.291
<i>For you?</i>

39:07.375 --> 39:10.666
<i>Do this one thing,</i>
<i>and I can give you $15 million.</i>

39:10.750 --> 39:12.458
<i>-Fifteen million?</i>
<i>-Fifteen…</i>

39:12.541 --> 39:14.583
<i>You don't have $15 million.</i>

39:14.666 --> 39:18.083
<i>If you do this one thing for me, I will.</i>

39:20.541 --> 39:22.875
<i>I know this</i>
<i>is not gonna make up for what I did…</i>

39:22.958 --> 39:24.875
<i>-[scoffs]</i>
<i>-…or what type of father I was.</i>

39:24.958 --> 39:25.833
<i>Yeah.</i>

39:25.916 --> 39:28.291
<i>With $15 million,</i>
<i>you can help these people.</i>

39:28.375 --> 39:30.541
<i>You can go back to school,</i>
<i>do whatever you want.</i>

39:30.625 --> 39:34.125
<i>Whatever you do with this money,</i>
<i>I know will be the right thing.</i>

39:36.583 --> 39:39.000
<i>[woman speaking indistinctly over PA]</i>

39:47.166 --> 39:48.250
<i>What one thing?</i>

40:19.291 --> 40:21.416
<i>[Geeta] Hey. Please! Hey. Hey.</i>

40:21.500 --> 40:22.625
<i>You're the coyote, right?</i>

40:25.291 --> 40:27.583
<i>Take us in. Please.</i>

40:29.166 --> 40:30.166
<i>Please.</i>

40:31.208 --> 40:32.291
<i>[gun firing]</i>

40:34.625 --> 40:35.500
<i>[sighs in relief]</i>

40:35.583 --> 40:37.375
<i>Not bad for your first time.</i>

40:38.541 --> 40:40.958
<i>-[chuckles]</i>
<i>-Okay, I get it. I understand.</i>

40:41.041 --> 40:44.083
<i>I understand</i>
<i>what beautiful little machine. [chuckles]</i>

40:44.166 --> 40:45.625
<i>Hey, don't point a gun at me.</i>

40:46.500 --> 40:47.708
<i>Sorry. Sorry.</i>

40:49.958 --> 40:51.708
<i>Whoo!</i>

40:51.791 --> 40:53.708
<i>[vehicle approaching]</i>

40:54.750 --> 40:55.791
<i>[Scott] Here comes our ride.</i>

40:55.875 --> 40:59.125
<i>-Oh, good. You want some water?</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

41:14.000 --> 41:16.041
<i>You're kidding. What is this?</i>

41:16.125 --> 41:16.958
<i>What?</i>

41:17.041 --> 41:18.833
<i>I swear to God, if this whole mission</i>

41:18.916 --> 41:21.833
<i>is some insane way</i>
<i>for you to reconnect with your daughter--</i>

41:21.916 --> 41:23.708
<i>It's not, all right? Trust me.</i>

41:23.791 --> 41:26.458
<i>She's a volunteer at the camp.</i>
<i>She's got connections.</i>

41:27.125 --> 41:29.500
<i>She's just giving us a ride</i>
<i>into the quarantine zone.</i>

41:29.583 --> 41:31.708
<i>You really think</i>
<i>I'd take her inside the city?</i>

41:31.791 --> 41:32.750
<i>[sighs]</i>

41:32.833 --> 41:35.291
<i>["The End" by The Raveonettes playing]</i>

41:37.333 --> 41:39.458
<i>♪ This is the end ♪</i>

41:40.250 --> 41:42.750
<i>♪ Beautiful friend ♪</i>

41:46.291 --> 41:49.125
<i>♪ This is the end ♪</i>

41:49.208 --> 41:53.541
<i>♪ My only friend, the end… ♪</i>

41:53.625 --> 41:56.833
<i>Hey, how you doing? I don't think</i>
<i>we've officially met. My name's Martin.</i>

41:56.916 --> 42:00.041
<i>Don't talk to me. I don't trust</i>
<i>these people, especially you.</i>

42:00.666 --> 42:02.875
<i>-Oh.</i>
<i>-You stay the hell away from me.</i>

42:02.958 --> 42:03.875
<i>Yes, ma'am.</i>

42:08.166 --> 42:09.083
<i>Ooh.</i>

42:09.708 --> 42:11.625
<i>[laughs]</i>

42:11.708 --> 42:13.625
<i>♪ …what will it be? ♪</i>

42:13.708 --> 42:18.208
<i>♪ So limitless and free ♪</i>

42:19.333 --> 42:22.291
<i>♪ Desperately in need ♪</i>

42:22.958 --> 42:27.708
<i>♪ Of some stranger's hand ♪</i>

42:27.791 --> 42:32.041
<i>♪ In a desperate land… ♪</i>

42:34.083 --> 42:37.000
<i>[man over PA] </i>Detainees at
the Las Vegas McCarran Quarantine Center,

42:37.083 --> 42:41.083
<i>this facility will be closed</i>
<i>by the end of the day. No personnel…</i>

42:41.166 --> 42:43.375
<i>[announcement continues indistinctly]</i>

42:52.250 --> 42:54.916
<i>Criminals, meet your coyote.</i>

42:55.666 --> 42:56.958
<i>Does coyote girl have a name?</i>

42:57.041 --> 42:59.375
<i>Lilly, but "coyote" sounds cool.</i>

42:59.458 --> 43:01.166
<i>You can just call me that if you want.</i>

43:01.708 --> 43:03.750
<i>All right, I'll leave you guys to it.</i>

43:03.833 --> 43:05.875
<i>I'll meet you outside Barstow in 24 hours.</i>

43:05.958 --> 43:07.500
<i>-Okay?</i>
<i>-Okay.</i>

43:08.750 --> 43:10.083
<i>Try not to get nuked</i>

43:10.166 --> 43:12.000
<i>or murdered by the undead.</i>

43:12.916 --> 43:15.291
<i>[woman speaking Spanish over PA]</i>

43:20.958 --> 43:22.333
<i>[girl crying]</i>

43:27.750 --> 43:30.458
<i>[Kate] Hey. Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey.</i>
<i>What's wrong?</i>

43:30.541 --> 43:31.666
<i>Mom's gone.</i>

43:33.125 --> 43:34.083
<i>[sighs]</i>

43:38.708 --> 43:39.916
<i>[sighs]</i>

43:40.000 --> 43:42.291
<i>-[Vanderohe] Here.</i>
<i>-Um…</i>

43:42.833 --> 43:43.750
<i>Question.</i>

43:44.416 --> 43:45.291
<i>Yes, Dieter.</i>

43:45.375 --> 43:47.916
<i>You don't think I need something bigger?</i>

43:49.000 --> 43:51.416
<i>If I give you something bigger than that,</i>
<i>you're already dead.</i>

43:52.041 --> 43:52.875
<i>Dead?</i>

43:53.375 --> 43:55.083
<i>Auf Wiedersehen,</i> dead.

43:58.166 --> 43:59.958
<i>Um, this belongs to where?</i>

44:03.666 --> 44:05.291
<i>Give me a fucking break. Really?</i>

44:05.375 --> 44:07.958
<i>Dieter, try not to piss Van off.</i>

44:09.000 --> 44:09.833
<i>Thank you, sir.</i>

44:13.875 --> 44:14.708
<i>Hey.</i>

44:14.791 --> 44:16.875
<i>-What did you do?</i>
<i>-What do you mean?</i>

44:16.958 --> 44:18.250
<i>[both grunting]</i>

44:18.333 --> 44:19.583
<i>[Kate] Stop!</i>

44:19.666 --> 44:20.666
<i>Get off me!</i>

44:21.333 --> 44:22.958
<i>-Stop!</i>
<i>-What the hell's going on?</i>

44:23.041 --> 44:24.208
<i>The hell are you doing?</i>

44:25.291 --> 44:26.833
<i>[Kate] You took her in.</i>

44:26.916 --> 44:28.375
<i>You took in Geeta.</i>

44:28.458 --> 44:31.250
<i>-</i>Yeah. I took her in. Her and two others.
-[gasps]

44:31.333 --> 44:34.666
<i>I take a lot of people in.</i>
<i>They need that money to get out of here.</i>

44:34.750 --> 44:36.208
<i>-You know that.</i>
<i>-She didn't come back.</i>

44:36.291 --> 44:38.083
<i>Well, not everyone does.</i>

44:38.166 --> 44:40.125
<i>-They know the risks.</i>
<i>-[Kate] She has two kids!</i>

44:44.666 --> 44:46.541
<i>-[Lilly] She didn't tell me that.</i>
<i>-[scoffs]</i>

44:47.166 --> 44:50.041
<i>Listen, if I knew she had kids,</i>
<i>I wouldn't have taken her.</i>

44:51.750 --> 44:53.083
<i>Did you see her die?</i>

44:54.250 --> 44:55.208
<i>No.</i>

44:56.458 --> 44:58.541
<i>They went ahead. I… I hung back.</i>

45:00.416 --> 45:03.041
<i>They never came out. I'm sorry.</i>

45:04.916 --> 45:07.500
<i>I waited, Kate, as long as I could,</i>
<i>but at the end of the day--</i>

45:07.583 --> 45:08.875
<i>I'm coming with you.</i>

45:11.291 --> 45:12.833
<i>-No, you're not.</i>
<i>-Yes, I am.</i>

45:12.916 --> 45:14.958
<i>We're not having this conversation.</i>
<i>You're not coming.</i>

45:15.041 --> 45:18.708
<i>There are two kids</i>
<i>whose mother is lost in there.</i>

45:18.791 --> 45:21.041
<i>Two kids that I help look out for.</i>

45:21.125 --> 45:22.166
<i>I have to find her.</i>

45:22.250 --> 45:24.541
<i>Well, tell us what she looks like.</i>
<i>We'll look out for her.</i>

45:24.625 --> 45:26.625
<i>-You think I trust you to do that?</i>
<i>-Kate!</i>

45:27.250 --> 45:29.500
<i>-You're not coming!</i>
<i>-I'm not asking you!</i>

45:29.583 --> 45:31.375
<i>I'm telling you what's gonna happen.</i>

45:31.458 --> 45:32.458
<i>Come here.</i>

45:34.708 --> 45:38.333
<i>Listen to me. As someone</i>
<i>who's seen what this looks like,</i>

45:38.416 --> 45:41.541
<i>this is not a path you wanna go down.</i>
<i>I'm not gonna let you try.</i>

45:42.166 --> 45:43.375
<i>You're gonna stay put.</i>

45:43.458 --> 45:46.083
<i>We'll look for your friend.</i>
<i>I'll see you when we get out.</i>

45:46.166 --> 45:49.416
<i>-Okay?</i>
<i>-No. No, not okay.</i>

45:49.500 --> 45:50.416
<i>You listen.</i>

45:51.041 --> 45:52.291
<i>I'm going in either way.</i>

45:52.875 --> 45:55.166
<i>I can go in with you,</i>
<i>and you can keep me safe.</i>

45:55.250 --> 45:58.916
<i>-Kate.</i>
<i>-Or-- Or… I'll just sneak in after you,</i>

45:59.708 --> 46:00.916
<i>and I'll probably die.</i>

46:02.000 --> 46:03.375
<i>The choice is yours.</i>

46:05.375 --> 46:07.208
<i>What's it gonna be, Dad?</i>

46:14.000 --> 46:14.833
<i>[exhales deeply]</i>

46:21.083 --> 46:23.000
<i>If we see your friend, great.</i>

46:23.791 --> 46:27.500
<i>But you are not to run off</i>
<i>looking for her. This is life or death.</i>

46:27.583 --> 46:31.125
<i>And if you screw around,</i>
<i>some of these people are gonna die.</i>

46:31.208 --> 46:32.208
<i>You understand that?</i>

46:32.291 --> 46:33.958
<i>And they've got families too.</i>

46:34.625 --> 46:38.833
<i>So you are never, ever to leave my sight.</i>

46:38.916 --> 46:40.666
<i>Those are my terms. Are we clear?</i>

46:43.250 --> 46:45.541
<i>Yeah. We're clear.</i>

46:49.125 --> 46:51.708
<i>Guys, this is Kate,</i>

46:52.333 --> 46:53.916
<i>newest member of the team.</i>

46:54.583 --> 46:56.500
<i>-Hey. Hello.</i>
<i>-How's it going?</i>

46:57.583 --> 46:59.125
<i>Scott, what the fuck?</i>

47:01.250 --> 47:03.916
<i>[officer] You having a good time?</i>
<i>What's he talking about?</i>

47:04.000 --> 47:07.041
<i>The bomb that's coming to kill you?</i>
<i>Is that what you're talking about?</i>

47:07.125 --> 47:08.500
<i>That's the last bus.</i>

47:08.583 --> 47:10.958
<i>Go, Speedy Gonzales! </i>Arriba.

47:11.041 --> 47:13.500
<i>[man over PA] </i>This is
a mandatory evacuation zone.

47:14.166 --> 47:16.708
<i>-We're going to need one more guy.</i>
<i>-For what?</i>

47:16.791 --> 47:19.458
<i>You don't know what it's like</i>
<i>in there. Not anymore.</i>

47:19.541 --> 47:22.666
<i>-The team's big enough--</i>
<i>-Trust me. We need another person.</i>

47:25.958 --> 47:27.458
<i>What the hell's going on here?</i>

47:32.166 --> 47:33.750
<i>You want to make 20 grand?</i>

47:33.833 --> 47:35.125
<i>Twenty thousand dollars?</i>

47:36.875 --> 47:38.750
<i>Yeah, I'll make 20 fucking grand.</i>

47:43.000 --> 47:45.791
<i>I don't fucking get it.</i>
<i>Why the fuck would she bring him?</i>

47:45.875 --> 47:48.333
<i>Honey, easy with the f-bombs, okay?</i>

47:48.416 --> 47:49.875
<i>-[Kate] Are you kidding?</i>
<i>-[officer] Chainsaw.</i>

47:49.958 --> 47:53.375
<i>We're about to march into a sea</i>
<i>of dead people and commit grand larceny.</i>

47:53.458 --> 47:55.833
<i>-But excuse me for swearing.</i>
<i>-That's for you.</i>

47:55.916 --> 47:57.916
<i>[officer] Me? [chuckles] Oh, yes.</i>

47:58.583 --> 47:59.916
<i>[exclaims]</i>

48:00.541 --> 48:01.416
<i>I got this.</i>

48:02.708 --> 48:03.833
<i>Whoo!</i>

48:03.916 --> 48:05.458
<i>We're gonna have some fun, yeah?</i>

48:06.958 --> 48:09.958
<i>I'm telling you,</i>
<i>you got the right guy for this.</i>

48:11.333 --> 48:15.208
<i>And also, if you happen</i>
<i>to get scared in there or nervous,</i>

48:15.291 --> 48:16.875
<i>I want you to stay close to me.</i>

48:16.958 --> 48:18.750
<i>-Mm-hmm.</i>
<i>-I got you.</i>

48:18.833 --> 48:19.958
<i>-Thanks.</i>
<i>-[gun cocking]</i>

48:23.208 --> 48:24.291
<i>What's up, bro?</i>

48:25.083 --> 48:27.041
<i>Gas tank. You carry that.</i>

48:29.958 --> 48:33.541
<i>Don't ever touch my saw again, okay?</i>
<i>Don't ever talk to her again…</i>

48:35.708 --> 48:36.833
<i>bro.</i>

48:38.291 --> 48:40.791
<i>-Okay. For sure.</i>
<i>-[Vanderohe] Good answer.</i>

48:42.250 --> 48:44.041
<i>[Lilly] All right, guys, let's go!</i>

48:50.833 --> 48:52.250
<i>The fuck you looking at?</i>

48:53.666 --> 48:55.041
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

49:07.666 --> 49:09.833
<i>[wind howling]</i>

49:21.583 --> 49:22.458
<i>Behind me.</i>

49:30.458 --> 49:32.750
<i>Put your gun up, idiot.</i>

49:34.250 --> 49:35.875
<i>Hey. It's not too late to go back.</i>

49:51.666 --> 49:54.500
<i>[Lilly] There they are, the shamblers,</i>

49:55.458 --> 49:56.583
<i>what's left of them.</i>

49:57.250 --> 49:58.125
<i>[Dieter sighs]</i>

49:59.958 --> 50:01.666
<i>What happened to them exactly?</i>

50:01.750 --> 50:03.000
<i>[Lilly] What's it look like?</i>

50:03.083 --> 50:05.291
<i>Weren't smart enough</i>
<i>to get out of the sun.</i>

50:05.375 --> 50:07.666
<i>You should see what happens when it rains.</i>

50:07.750 --> 50:09.958
<i>For a few hours,</i>
<i>they all come back to life.</i>

50:11.583 --> 50:12.625
<i>Oh, </i>Scheisse!

50:14.125 --> 50:15.541
<i>Okay, let's go. Come on.</i>

50:16.833 --> 50:19.000
<i>How… how much rain is…</i>

50:19.083 --> 50:20.125
<i>[Chambers] Let's get this.</i>

50:20.708 --> 50:21.958
<i>Tourists.</i>

50:22.041 --> 50:23.708
<i>-[growls]</i>
<i>-[camera shutter clicks]</i>

50:26.041 --> 50:28.125
<i>Hey, you're Lilly, right?</i>

50:30.083 --> 50:31.875
<i>You sure know your way around here.</i>

50:31.958 --> 50:33.333
<i>Well, what's it to you?</i>

50:33.416 --> 50:34.833
<i>Well, maybe a lot.</i>

50:36.166 --> 50:38.333
<i>How much you know</i>
<i>about how these things operate?</i>

50:38.416 --> 50:39.625
<i>Everything there is.</i>

50:40.333 --> 50:42.083
<i>-Hmm.</i>
<i>-[Lilly] Why?</i>

50:43.083 --> 50:45.500
<i>[chuckles] Good to know.</i>

51:04.083 --> 51:05.458
<i>[Dieter] Wow, </i>was ist das?

51:08.125 --> 51:10.208
<i>[Chambers] Holy shit. What is all this?</i>

51:10.291 --> 51:11.458
<i>[Kate] What happened here?</i>

51:11.541 --> 51:13.916
<i>[Lilly] Where the police</i>
<i>and military finally fell.</i>

51:14.000 --> 51:15.458
<i>-Vegas' last stand.</i>
<i>-[growling deeply]</i>

51:15.541 --> 51:18.708
<i>-[Guzman] Whoa, whoa. Everybody be quiet.</i>
<i>-[growling]</i>

51:18.791 --> 51:20.000
<i>Do you hear that?</i>

51:20.083 --> 51:21.000
<i>[speaks French]</i>

51:22.625 --> 51:25.291
<i>-What the hell is that?</i>
<i>-Get behind the car! Go!</i>

51:25.375 --> 51:27.208
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

51:28.208 --> 51:30.041
<i>[growling continues]</i>

51:42.625 --> 51:43.541
<i>What is this?</i>

51:44.166 --> 51:45.166
<i>Valentine.</i>

51:45.750 --> 51:46.833
<i>Valentine?</i>

51:51.833 --> 51:53.333
<i>[roaring]</i>

51:53.416 --> 51:55.166
<i>[Martin] It's a goddamn zombie tiger.</i>

51:56.291 --> 51:57.583
<i>That's crossing the line.</i>

52:01.958 --> 52:04.083
<i>-[Chambers] Hell, yeah.</i>
<i>-[Guzman] Awesome.</i>

52:04.708 --> 52:05.750
<i>[chuckles]</i>

52:09.541 --> 52:11.041
<i>[growling]</i>

52:33.583 --> 52:34.625
<i>Clear.</i>

52:34.708 --> 52:36.250
<i>-Los geht's.</i>
-[Dieter] Okay.

52:40.041 --> 52:41.125
<i>[officer] The hell was that?</i>

52:41.208 --> 52:43.000
<i>She was one of Siegfried and Roy's.</i>

52:43.083 --> 52:44.833
<i>She guards</i>
<i>the beginning of their territory.</i>

52:45.625 --> 52:48.208
<i>-Is there another way around?</i>
<i>-Not really.</i>

52:48.291 --> 52:49.666
<i>[indistinct chattering]</i>

52:55.416 --> 52:57.625
<i>Hey, Cummings.</i>
<i>Let me see your gun for a second.</i>

52:57.708 --> 52:59.208
<i>What? No shot.</i>

52:59.291 --> 53:00.666
<i>[Lilly] Just for a second.</i>

53:01.833 --> 53:04.291
<i>I like it. It's beautiful.</i>

53:06.416 --> 53:07.458
<i>It's reliable too.</i>

53:08.041 --> 53:09.583
<i>-Oh, yeah?</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

53:13.291 --> 53:14.416
<i>Can I touch it?</i>

53:15.500 --> 53:17.291
<i>-You wanna touch it?</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

53:19.416 --> 53:21.000
<i>Just for a second.</i>

53:21.625 --> 53:23.125
<i>Just for a second.</i>

53:23.208 --> 53:24.500
<i>[Cummings] Mmm.</i>

53:33.791 --> 53:35.041
<i>-[Cummings] Oh, my…</i>
<i>-[Peters] Hey!</i>

53:35.125 --> 53:37.875
<i>I would say I was hoping I wouldn't</i>
<i>have to do that, but I'd be lying.</i>

53:37.958 --> 53:40.000
<i>-What are you talking about?</i>
<i>-What is she doing?</i>

53:40.083 --> 53:41.541
<i>She just shot me. Shoot her!</i>

53:41.625 --> 53:44.791
<i>They'll know we're here. They won't care</i>
<i>so long as we play by their rules.</i>

53:44.875 --> 53:47.500
<i>-Rules? </i>De qué habla esta pendeja?
<i>-[Guzman] </i>O sea, está loca.

53:47.583 --> 53:49.666
<i>If we wanna go further,</i>
<i>we have to make a trade.</i>

53:49.750 --> 53:51.125
<i>-Trade? Really?</i>
<i>-[Cummings] No trade!</i>

53:51.208 --> 53:54.166
<i>Yes. An offering to show our subservience.</i>

53:54.250 --> 53:56.208
<i>-They don't think.</i>
<i>-[Cummings] Shoot this bitch!</i>

53:56.291 --> 53:58.333
<i>-If they come, we kill them.</i>
<i>-[Lilly] You don't understand.</i>

53:58.416 --> 54:01.208
<i>-They're not what you think they are.</i>
<i>-[Cummings] Shoot her in the face!</i>

54:01.291 --> 54:04.375
<i>-[screaming]</i>
<i>-We're not talking about shamblers here.</i>

54:04.458 --> 54:06.083
<i>You're right. They don't think.</i>

54:06.166 --> 54:09.291
<i>They just move and eat.</i>
<i>But we're talking about the other ones.</i>

54:09.375 --> 54:13.041
<i>-The alphas.</i>
<i>-Yes. They're smarter. They're faster.</i>

54:13.125 --> 54:16.041
<i>They're organized.</i>
<i>Straight out of your fucking nightmares.</i>

54:16.125 --> 54:17.166
<i>[Cummings] Please.</i>

54:17.250 --> 54:20.250
<i>You all keep talking</i>
<i>about the city like it's their prison.</i>

54:20.333 --> 54:22.166
<i>It's not. It's their kingdom.</i>

54:22.750 --> 54:24.416
<i>They won't mind us</i>
<i>poking around the outside</i>

54:24.500 --> 54:26.166
<i>so long as we play by their rules.</i>

54:26.250 --> 54:28.625
<i>-[Cummings] Oh my God!</i>
<i>-We're moving into the heart of it now.</i>

54:28.708 --> 54:30.208
<i>I have a mother. I love her.</i>

54:30.291 --> 54:31.958
<i>Well, everyone has a mom, you cunt,</i>

54:32.041 --> 54:35.458
<i>but not everyone is an abuser</i>
<i>lording power over quarantined women.</i>

54:35.541 --> 54:37.750
<i>[Cummings sobbing] She's lying!</i>
<i>That's not true.</i>

54:37.833 --> 54:40.375
<i>[Lilly] Shut your mouth.</i>
<i>I've seen what you've done to those women.</i>

54:40.458 --> 54:42.625
<i>-[kick thuds]</i>
<i>-You fucking rapist.</i>

54:42.708 --> 54:45.041
<i>[Cummings] Oh my God!</i>
<i>That's not true at all.</i>

54:45.125 --> 54:46.750
<i>[screeching in the distance]</i>

54:46.833 --> 54:48.541
<i>-Oh, fuck, no! No!</i>
<i>-She's coming.</i>

54:48.625 --> 54:50.333
<i>[Cummings] Who's coming? What's coming?</i>

54:50.416 --> 54:53.541
<i>-She? What's she?</i>
<i>-[Cummings] No, please. We bonded. Please.</i>

54:54.125 --> 54:56.500
<i>No. No, no, no. Don't trust her.</i>

54:56.583 --> 54:57.958
<i>-[Dieter] Sorry.</i>
<i>-[Cummings] No, please.</i>

54:58.041 --> 55:00.958
<i>Help me. Don't go. No, we're a team.</i>

55:01.916 --> 55:03.291
<i>[growling]</i>

55:13.750 --> 55:14.916
<i>What the…</i>

55:16.083 --> 55:16.916
<i>[shushes]</i>

55:17.000 --> 55:19.083
<i>[growling and snarling]</i>

55:32.250 --> 55:34.458
<i>What… what the fuck?</i>

55:34.541 --> 55:37.083
<i>[growling and snarling]</i>

55:38.916 --> 55:40.375
<i>[sniffing]</i>

55:44.333 --> 55:45.458
<i>[screeching]</i>

55:47.666 --> 55:48.625
<i>Scheisse.</i>

55:50.500 --> 55:53.208
<i>Help. Shoot this!</i>
<i>What the fuck is this thing?</i>

55:53.291 --> 55:54.375
<i>[sniffing]</i>

55:55.250 --> 55:57.625
<i>Listen, no. No. Hi.</i>

55:58.375 --> 56:01.000
<i>-I'm not here to hurt you.</i>
<i>-[screeching]</i>

56:01.083 --> 56:04.250
<i>Come on.</i>
<i>Help me, help me, help me, help me.</i>

56:04.333 --> 56:06.291
<i>No! No, no, no, no, no.</i>

56:17.125 --> 56:18.375
<i>[screeches]</i>

56:18.458 --> 56:19.416
<i>[Cummings] Help me!</i>

56:20.625 --> 56:22.875
<i>Don't do it. Just stay away.</i>

56:24.083 --> 56:25.041
<i>What are you doing?</i>

56:34.166 --> 56:35.833
<i>[sobbing] No. Oh my God!</i>

56:37.625 --> 56:39.791
<i>Go away. Go over there. Go over there.</i>

56:43.708 --> 56:44.750
<i>[sobbing]</i>

56:45.833 --> 56:48.166
<i>[screaming] No!</i>

56:48.833 --> 56:50.791
<i>Help! No!</i>

56:51.708 --> 56:53.750
<i>[screeching]</i>

56:53.833 --> 56:57.833
<i>[Cummings screaming indistinctly]</i>

57:24.291 --> 57:25.291
<i>[grunts]</i>

57:27.166 --> 57:29.625
<i>-[Scott] You ever seen her kill anyone?</i>
<i>-[Lilly] Couple times.</i>

57:30.625 --> 57:32.416
<i>-[Cummings] No!</i>
<i>-[screeching]</i>

57:32.500 --> 57:33.666
<i>[Scott] Did they come back?</i>

57:33.750 --> 57:35.250
<i>[Lilly] Yep, as shamblers.</i>

57:36.000 --> 57:37.083
<i>[Cummings] No!</i>

57:37.166 --> 57:40.541
<i>[Lilly] My theory, this started</i>
<i>with one of them, an original.</i>

57:40.625 --> 57:42.083
<i>[Cummings] Oh, my God! No!</i>

57:42.166 --> 57:43.875
<i>[Lilly] Whoever that is, if he bites you--</i>

57:43.958 --> 57:45.666
<i>-[Vanderohe] Then you become an alpha.</i>
<i>-[Lilly] Exactly.</i>

57:45.750 --> 57:47.666
<i>Looks like</i>
<i>they're taking him to the Olympus.</i>

57:47.750 --> 57:49.875
<i>Good. Now we know where not to go.</i>

57:51.833 --> 57:54.291
<i>[Lilly] I've never figured out</i>
<i>exactly how it works.</i>

57:54.375 --> 57:57.958
<i>All I know is they take you in there,</i>
<i>and you come out like one of them,</i>

57:58.708 --> 58:00.250
<i>one of the fast ones.</i>

58:00.333 --> 58:02.916
<i>-So, they're taking him there to turn him.</i>
<i>-[Lilly] Yes.</i>

58:03.500 --> 58:05.958
<i>Scott, that could be where Geeta is.</i>

58:06.041 --> 58:08.000
<i>Kate, we've already talked about this.</i>

58:08.083 --> 58:10.166
<i>-[Kate] We have time.</i>
<i>-[Scott] It's not an option.</i>

58:10.250 --> 58:11.166
<i>Fine.</i>

58:11.791 --> 58:13.041
<i>That's what I thought.</i>

58:13.583 --> 58:16.708
<i>So, the shithead</i>
<i>buys us passage, and we keep going?</i>

58:16.791 --> 58:19.541
<i>Well, yeah.</i>
<i>The shithead should buy us some goodwill,</i>

58:19.625 --> 58:22.375
<i>but I'm not about to flaunt it</i>
<i>by walking on their streets.</i>

58:22.458 --> 58:24.583
<i>If we want to go further, we go indoors.</i>

58:24.666 --> 58:25.791
<i>Allez</i>, let's go.

58:27.500 --> 58:29.708
<i>[eerie music playing]</i>

58:47.583 --> 58:50.416
<i>Hey, uh, has there been</i>
<i>any thought given to triage?</i>

58:50.500 --> 58:51.333
<i>What do you mean?</i>

58:51.416 --> 58:55.500
<i>Well, I mean, obviously,</i>
<i>the German is the most important person</i>

58:55.583 --> 58:57.208
<i>'cause he can open the safe,</i>

58:57.291 --> 59:00.875
<i>but barring that,</i>
<i>it's got to be me, right?</i>

59:00.958 --> 59:03.333
<i>Because without me,</i>
<i>you can't fly the chopper out of here.</i>

59:03.416 --> 59:06.083
<i>So that would make me</i>
<i>second most important.</i>

59:06.166 --> 59:10.000
<i>And I don't know if you two</i>
<i>are tied for third or whatever,</i>

59:10.083 --> 59:13.750
<i>but I'm certainly</i>
<i>more important than that guy.</i>

59:13.833 --> 59:16.083
<i>Sorry. I didn't know</i>
<i>you were listening. I am way…</i>

59:16.166 --> 59:19.750
<i>[chuckles] Okay, I am definitely</i>
<i>more important than that guy.</i>

59:19.833 --> 59:21.208
<i>I don't trust that guy.</i>

59:21.291 --> 59:22.708
<i>You know why he was hired?</i>

59:22.791 --> 59:24.708
<i>He was hired to keep tabs on us</i>

59:24.791 --> 59:27.625
<i>for when we open the safe,</i>
<i>that we didn't take the money and run.</i>

59:28.250 --> 59:29.458
<i>We should be incentivized.</i>

59:30.125 --> 59:31.500
<i>I'm not trying to be the bad guy,</i>

59:31.583 --> 59:33.708
<i>but we should be incentivized</i>

59:33.791 --> 59:35.708
<i>to let him die.</i>

59:41.083 --> 59:44.041
<i>What? What's everybody looking at me for?</i>

59:45.375 --> 59:48.583
<i>It's a free country.</i>
<i>People can look at whoever they want.</i>

59:48.666 --> 59:51.791
<i>Actually, it's not a free country.</i>
<i>We're not in America anymore.</i>

59:51.875 --> 59:52.750
<i>Haven't you heard?</i>

59:52.833 --> 59:56.833
<i>Which technically makes it</i>
<i>an even freer country, right?</i>

1:00:00.083 --> 1:00:01.125
<i>Whatever.</i>

1:00:01.208 --> 1:00:03.041
<i>[all snarling and growling]</i>

1:00:03.125 --> 1:00:06.250
<i>What the fuck is this?</i>
<i>[shouting indistinctly]</i>

1:00:11.125 --> 1:00:12.291
<i>Stay away from me!</i>

1:00:16.333 --> 1:00:17.666
<i>[shouting indistinctly]</i>

1:00:19.041 --> 1:00:19.916
<i>[screams]</i>

1:00:25.791 --> 1:00:28.083
<i>[snarling loudly]</i>

1:00:36.666 --> 1:00:38.958
<i>[screeching]</i>

1:00:39.041 --> 1:00:40.416
<i>What the fuck?</i>

1:00:40.500 --> 1:00:42.208
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

1:00:58.041 --> 1:00:59.250
<i>What is that?</i>

1:01:00.416 --> 1:01:01.958
<i>[snarling softly]</i>

1:01:11.000 --> 1:01:12.958
<i>-[growling]</i>
<i>-No.</i>

1:01:14.000 --> 1:01:15.125
<i>[laughing]</i>

1:01:16.208 --> 1:01:17.166
<i>Hey.</i>

1:01:18.458 --> 1:01:20.375
<i>Hey. Let me talk to you for a second.</i>

1:01:20.458 --> 1:01:23.958
<i>-I can help you. Just let me--</i>
<i>-[snarls loudly]</i>

1:01:26.250 --> 1:01:28.041
<i>Okay. Okay.</i>

1:01:34.166 --> 1:01:35.375
<i>[both snarling softly]</i>

1:01:46.166 --> 1:01:47.166
<i>[screeches]</i>

1:01:50.833 --> 1:01:52.000
<i>What the fuck?</i>

1:01:56.958 --> 1:01:59.166
<i>[all growling]</i>

1:02:02.041 --> 1:02:02.916
<i>No.</i>

1:02:04.416 --> 1:02:05.333
<i>No.</i>

1:02:07.208 --> 1:02:10.041
<i>No. No, no!</i>

1:02:10.625 --> 1:02:12.500
<i>Okay. Okay, look.</i>

1:02:12.583 --> 1:02:15.083
<i>Let's just talk turkey for a second. I--</i>

1:02:15.166 --> 1:02:16.583
<i>-[screams]</i>
<i>-[all growling]</i>

1:02:19.666 --> 1:02:21.166
<i>-[roaring]</i>
<i>-[screaming]</i>

1:02:28.375 --> 1:02:30.333
<i>[screaming]</i>

1:02:37.875 --> 1:02:41.458
<i>-[all snarling and screeching]</i>
<i>-[Cummings screaming]</i>

1:02:54.291 --> 1:02:55.250
<i>[Dieter] Oh, shit.</i>

1:03:00.875 --> 1:03:02.208
<i>[screams]</i>

1:03:02.791 --> 1:03:03.833
<i>[whispers] Don't touch them.</i>

1:03:06.583 --> 1:03:08.416
<i>Don't shine the light in their eyes.</i>

1:03:09.583 --> 1:03:11.708
<i>I've seen this before.</i>
<i>They're hibernating.</i>

1:03:12.791 --> 1:03:15.791
<i>If we can't see them,</i>
<i>how are we supposed to move forward?</i>

1:03:17.000 --> 1:03:18.208
<i>I'll mark us a path.</i>

1:03:20.833 --> 1:03:21.958
<i>[cracks glow stick]</i>

1:03:25.291 --> 1:03:26.416
<i>[eerie music playing]</i>

1:03:41.875 --> 1:03:42.708
<i>Go for it.</i>

1:03:43.375 --> 1:03:45.458
<i>Why? You want to check out my ass?</i>

1:03:45.541 --> 1:03:48.916
<i>No. I don't trust you</i>
<i>to have our backs if shit goes bad.</i>

1:03:49.000 --> 1:03:51.666
<i>I've been watching you,</i>
<i>and you're up to something.</i>

1:03:51.750 --> 1:03:53.083
<i>When we all get to the casino,</i>

1:03:53.166 --> 1:03:54.875
<i>I think we need</i>
<i>to have a little conversation</i>

1:03:54.958 --> 1:03:57.166
<i>about what exactly your role is here.</i>

1:03:57.250 --> 1:03:58.458
<i>Knock yourself out.</i>

1:04:05.666 --> 1:04:07.333
<i>[snarling softly]</i>

1:04:30.916 --> 1:04:32.208
<i>Gotcha, bitch.</i>

1:04:57.916 --> 1:04:59.833
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

1:05:36.666 --> 1:05:37.916
<i>[growling]</i>

1:05:39.458 --> 1:05:40.583
<i>[groans]</i>

1:05:45.375 --> 1:05:46.791
<i>[wheezing]</i>

1:06:25.833 --> 1:06:28.833
<i>[growling and wheezing softly]</i>

1:06:41.916 --> 1:06:43.791
<i>[objects clattering]</i>

1:06:52.666 --> 1:06:54.083
<i>[screaming]</i>

1:06:58.166 --> 1:06:59.666
<i>[Chambers continues screaming]</i>

1:07:06.458 --> 1:07:08.125
<i>-[screaming]</i>
<i>-[all growling]</i>

1:08:37.000 --> 1:08:39.416
<i>-You motherfucker.</i>
<i>-[trigger clicking]</i>

1:08:41.750 --> 1:08:42.625
<i>Bitch.</i>

1:08:43.416 --> 1:08:44.541
<i>Fuck!</i>

1:08:44.625 --> 1:08:45.541
<i>[gun firing]</i>

1:08:45.625 --> 1:08:46.625
<i>[Chambers grunting]</i>

1:08:53.708 --> 1:08:54.833
<i>This way!</i>

1:09:03.250 --> 1:09:05.458
<i>-Where's Chambers?</i>
<i>-[Martin] She was right behind me.</i>

1:09:05.541 --> 1:09:08.166
<i>-What happened? What did you do?</i>
<i>-I didn't do anything.</i>

1:09:08.250 --> 1:09:10.083
<i>She started shooting.</i>
<i>I wasn't close to her.</i>

1:09:10.166 --> 1:09:12.583
<i>Bullshit! She was back there</i>
<i>with you! I know she was!</i>

1:09:12.666 --> 1:09:13.916
<i>-Buddy…</i>
<i>-What happened?</i>

1:09:14.000 --> 1:09:15.458
<i>-You don't want to--</i>
<i>-Motherfucker!</i>

1:09:26.833 --> 1:09:29.708
<i>She's gone! Come on.</i>
<i>Leave her! She's dead!</i>

1:09:30.958 --> 1:09:33.791
<i>Chambers! Chambers!</i>

1:09:35.500 --> 1:09:36.583
<i>Come on!</i>

1:09:41.833 --> 1:09:43.041
<i>[Chambers screaming]</i>

1:09:50.916 --> 1:09:51.916
<i>Go!</i>

1:09:52.000 --> 1:09:54.958
<i>Run! Run!</i>

1:09:55.041 --> 1:09:57.208
<i>[dramatic music playing]</i>

1:10:22.375 --> 1:10:24.291
<i>[Scott] Guz, come on. Let's go.</i>

1:10:25.208 --> 1:10:28.166
<i>Guzman. Guz! She's gone.</i>

1:10:28.250 --> 1:10:30.250
<i>We gotta move. Come on, move!</i>

1:11:37.708 --> 1:11:39.000
<i>[snarling]</i>

1:11:49.000 --> 1:11:49.875
<i>[zombie 1 snarls]</i>

1:11:53.625 --> 1:11:54.750
<i>[zombie 2 snarls]</i>

1:11:58.083 --> 1:11:59.500
<i>[zombie 3 snarls]</i>

1:12:01.458 --> 1:12:02.291
<i>[Kate] Lilly.</i>

1:12:03.250 --> 1:12:04.083
<i>[gun fires]</i>

1:12:04.583 --> 1:12:06.041
<i>There's no way Geeta's alive, right?</i>

1:12:06.125 --> 1:12:07.750
<i>I mean, look at these things.</i>

1:12:08.625 --> 1:12:10.916
<i>Don't be so sure. I brought a guy in once.</i>

1:12:11.000 --> 1:12:13.500
<i>Lost sight of him.</i>
<i>Had to leave him. I thought he was dead.</i>

1:12:13.583 --> 1:12:16.416
<i>Then three days later,</i>
<i>he came walking back out.</i>

1:12:19.041 --> 1:12:20.166
<i>What happened to him?</i>

1:12:21.125 --> 1:12:22.875
<i>[Lilly] Said they took him to the Olympus.</i>

1:12:22.958 --> 1:12:25.208
<i>Shoved him in a room</i>
<i>with two other people.</i>

1:12:25.291 --> 1:12:27.416
<i>The leader, he came for them one by one.</i>

1:12:28.291 --> 1:12:30.750
<i>If my guy hadn't escaped,</i>
<i>he would have been next.</i>

1:12:32.166 --> 1:12:34.041
<i>So that's a pretty common theme for you?</i>

1:12:34.125 --> 1:12:35.500
<i>Leaving people behind.</i>

1:12:36.083 --> 1:12:38.291
<i>Do you think</i>
<i>I enjoy having to leave people?</i>

1:12:40.208 --> 1:12:42.333
<i>I'm doing what I can to make things right.</i>

1:12:54.125 --> 1:12:55.166
<i>[Dieter] Sir.</i>

1:12:55.916 --> 1:12:57.333
<i>Come here. Look at this.</i>

1:12:58.625 --> 1:12:59.708
<i>[Maria] The hell?</i>

1:13:02.791 --> 1:13:03.625
<i>Is that…</i>

1:13:03.708 --> 1:13:06.666
<i>Yeah, another set</i>
<i>of blueprints to the safe.</i>

1:13:07.583 --> 1:13:09.458
<i>[whispers] Another set of blueprints.</i>

1:13:11.000 --> 1:13:12.833
<i>[Scott] Slimy bastard, Tanaka.</i>

1:13:14.291 --> 1:13:16.208
<i>Tanaka had other teams here before us.</i>

1:13:21.291 --> 1:13:22.708
<i>Do you know anything about this?</i>

1:13:24.625 --> 1:13:25.791
<i>That's news to me.</i>

1:13:32.333 --> 1:13:33.291
<i>[Scott sighs]</i>

1:13:34.708 --> 1:13:35.958
<i>Peters, get up to the roof.</i>

1:13:36.041 --> 1:13:39.375
<i>Get that chopper running</i>
<i>as fast as possible. Cruz, go with her.</i>

1:13:40.250 --> 1:13:41.541
<i>She talks too much.</i>

1:13:41.625 --> 1:13:44.166
<i>Look, I'm excited</i>
<i>to see my friends again, okay?</i>

1:13:44.250 --> 1:13:45.083
<i>Sue me.</i>

1:13:46.166 --> 1:13:49.458
<i>Me and the coyote will do</i>
<i>a perimeter check, board up the doors.</i>

1:13:49.541 --> 1:13:52.166
<i>Yeah. Kate and I</i>
<i>are gonna find the generators.</i>

1:13:52.250 --> 1:13:55.541
<i>Backup gennie's on the third-floor roof.</i>
<i>That's gonna be your safer bet.</i>

1:13:55.625 --> 1:13:56.958
<i>Third-floor roof. Got it.</i>

1:13:57.958 --> 1:13:59.291
<i>Van, get Dieter down to the vault.</i>

1:13:59.375 --> 1:14:00.666
<i>Take Guzman with you.</i>

1:14:00.750 --> 1:14:02.083
<i>Roger that.</i>

1:14:02.166 --> 1:14:07.041
<i>Dieter, access card for the outer doors</i>
<i>to the safe and the service elevators.</i>

1:14:07.125 --> 1:14:09.250
<i>It's by the cashiers windows that way.</i>

1:14:10.541 --> 1:14:12.416
<i>This should get you inside. Here.</i>

1:14:13.833 --> 1:14:14.666
<i>Thank you.</i>

1:14:15.541 --> 1:14:19.000
<i>[chuckles] That one's mine.</i>
<i>I got another one.</i>

1:14:19.083 --> 1:14:20.291
<i>[chuckles]</i>

1:14:22.416 --> 1:14:24.958
<i>All right. Everybody knows</i>
<i>what they're doing. Let's get it done.</i>

1:14:25.041 --> 1:14:25.916
<i>Yes, sir.</i>

1:14:30.208 --> 1:14:31.250
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

1:14:38.375 --> 1:14:40.083
<i>What a hunk of junk.</i>

1:14:42.375 --> 1:14:44.041
<i>No la vayas a cagar,</i> my friend.

1:14:44.750 --> 1:14:45.833
<i>[Peters] Right.</i>

1:14:46.666 --> 1:14:47.500
<i>Bye.</i>

1:14:51.000 --> 1:14:52.833
<i>What the hell is this?</i>

1:14:53.625 --> 1:14:56.500
<i>Spend all his money</i>
<i>on that fucking miniature?</i>

1:14:57.416 --> 1:14:58.333
<i>[growling]</i>

1:15:03.875 --> 1:15:05.166
<i>[roars]</i>

1:15:09.375 --> 1:15:11.000
<i>[Martin] I really hate that tiger.</i>

1:15:12.416 --> 1:15:13.833
<i>It's perverse.</i>

1:15:19.291 --> 1:15:20.166
<i>What was it?</i>

1:15:21.791 --> 1:15:23.625
<i>Guilt finally get the better of you?</i>

1:15:24.166 --> 1:15:26.041
<i>One too many out there to die?</i>

1:15:26.125 --> 1:15:28.000
<i>Matter of fact, yes, it has.</i>

1:15:29.208 --> 1:15:30.750
<i>That mom Kate's looking for,</i>

1:15:31.791 --> 1:15:33.333
<i>did you shoot her in the leg too?</i>

1:15:34.666 --> 1:15:36.708
<i>No, I just lost her.</i>

1:15:36.791 --> 1:15:39.250
<i>I've never left anyone I didn't have to</i>

1:15:40.125 --> 1:15:41.541
<i>or who didn't deserve it.</i>

1:15:41.625 --> 1:15:43.875
<i>You have no idea</i>
<i>what I've seen in those camps.</i>

1:15:43.958 --> 1:15:45.833
<i>What those people have to do to survive.</i>

1:15:45.916 --> 1:15:48.375
<i>At least within these walls,</i>
<i>the rules are clear.</i>

1:15:48.458 --> 1:15:50.500
<i>You don't see them</i>
<i>fucking each other over.</i>

1:15:51.250 --> 1:15:52.125
<i>[speaks French]</i>

1:15:56.000 --> 1:15:57.000
<i>If you screw me…</i>

1:16:01.833 --> 1:16:03.541
<i>two between the eyes.</i>

1:16:03.625 --> 1:16:04.708
<i>Two? Why two?</i>

1:16:05.500 --> 1:16:07.000
<i>The second one's just for fun.</i>

1:16:07.875 --> 1:16:09.375
<i>[Martin] Ah! Shit.</i>

1:16:12.625 --> 1:16:13.666
<i>What happens now?</i>

1:16:14.916 --> 1:16:15.750
<i>We wait.</i>

1:16:18.083 --> 1:16:20.041
<i>[Scott] You understand</i>
<i>that I had to do it, right?</i>

1:16:20.125 --> 1:16:20.958
<i>Do what?</i>

1:16:22.750 --> 1:16:23.583
<i>[Scott] Put her down.</i>

1:16:24.958 --> 1:16:29.125
<i>You know, all those things</i>
<i>they were saying… about me after.</i>

1:16:29.208 --> 1:16:31.625
<i>-I want to make sure you know I loved her.</i>
<i>-Yeah.</i>

1:16:32.250 --> 1:16:33.541
<i>We loved each other.</i>

1:16:36.791 --> 1:16:39.958
<i>If I ever made it seem</i>
<i>like that wasn't the case, I'm sorry.</i>

1:16:41.291 --> 1:16:42.750
<i>I got it. It's okay.</i>

1:16:44.875 --> 1:16:46.708
<i>-You do?</i>
<i>-[Kate] Yes.</i>

1:16:47.375 --> 1:16:48.208
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:16:49.250 --> 1:16:50.750
<i>You did what you had to do.</i>

1:16:51.625 --> 1:16:52.875
<i>She was one of them. It…</i>

1:16:53.708 --> 1:16:55.458
<i>It's fine. Okay?</i>

1:16:56.000 --> 1:16:57.708
<i>[breathes deeply]</i>

1:16:59.125 --> 1:16:59.958
<i>Wait.</i>

1:17:00.625 --> 1:17:04.458
<i>You think that's why I haven't</i>
<i>been talking to you all these years?</i>

1:17:05.708 --> 1:17:07.458
<i>Well, it seemed like the…</i>

1:17:08.375 --> 1:17:11.500
<i>-Seemed like the logical assumption. Yeah.</i>
<i>-[scoffs] No.</i>

1:17:12.125 --> 1:17:14.083
<i>What you did and what happened to her,</i>

1:17:15.333 --> 1:17:17.583
<i>I never blamed you for that, ever.</i>

1:17:18.375 --> 1:17:19.916
<i>Well, I don't… I don't get it.</i>

1:17:20.000 --> 1:17:22.416
<i>If it wasn't what happened,</i>
<i>what the hell was it?</i>

1:17:27.250 --> 1:17:28.166
<i>It's not the…</i>

1:17:29.250 --> 1:17:33.708
<i>It's not the fact that…</i>
<i>you killed my mother.</i>

1:17:40.333 --> 1:17:42.875
<i>It's that you never showed up after, okay?</i>

1:17:42.958 --> 1:17:44.333
<i>You… [sighs]</i>

1:17:45.000 --> 1:17:47.041
<i>You weren't there, Scott.</i>

1:17:47.125 --> 1:17:48.750
<i>You didn't call. You didn't visit.</i>

1:17:48.833 --> 1:17:51.666
<i>You didn't… talk about it.</i>

1:17:53.625 --> 1:17:54.791
<i>You didn't comfort me.</i>

1:17:59.000 --> 1:18:00.416
<i>[Scott] Yeah, you're right.</i>

1:18:01.166 --> 1:18:03.166
<i>It's 'cause every time I looked at you,</i>

1:18:03.958 --> 1:18:05.333
<i>I just saw her and…</i>

1:18:07.625 --> 1:18:08.875
<i>It hurt like hell.</i>

1:18:10.916 --> 1:18:11.750
<i>[sighs]</i>

1:18:14.416 --> 1:18:15.541
<i>Hurt like hell.</i>

1:18:19.000 --> 1:18:21.583
<i>And then when I tried</i>
<i>to come back around, you just…</i>

1:18:22.666 --> 1:18:26.375
<i>You seemed like you didn't want me there,</i>
<i>so I assumed I should stay gone.</i>

1:18:31.583 --> 1:18:33.625
<i>You know, maybe</i>
<i>there's a chance we could still…</i>

1:18:35.375 --> 1:18:36.208
<i>Still what?</i>

1:18:40.666 --> 1:18:41.500
<i>I don't know.</i>

1:18:43.750 --> 1:18:45.500
<i>Maybe you could look</i>
<i>into college somewhere.</i>

1:18:46.666 --> 1:18:49.083
<i>We shouldn't need money.</i>
<i>I could open a restaurant.</i>

1:18:50.083 --> 1:18:51.541
<i>A new food truck.</i>

1:18:52.791 --> 1:18:54.000
<i>Just have a life.</i>

1:18:54.708 --> 1:18:55.916
<i>I was thinking, uh…</i>

1:18:57.791 --> 1:19:00.250
<i>I was thinking</i>
<i>artisan grilled cheese sandwiches.</i>

1:19:01.041 --> 1:19:02.750
<i>Artisan grilled cheese?</i>

1:19:03.708 --> 1:19:05.000
<i>Yeah, what do you think?</i>

1:19:05.875 --> 1:19:06.791
<i>Mmm.</i>

1:19:10.833 --> 1:19:11.666
<i>Yeah, uh…</i>

1:19:13.166 --> 1:19:16.750
<i>[clears throat] I don't know.</i>
<i>It's a… it's a nice idea, but…</i>

1:19:22.166 --> 1:19:26.916
<i>I've spent so long hating you</i>
<i>that I can't just turn that off.</i>

1:19:29.666 --> 1:19:31.375
<i>I'm sorry. I'm sorry.</i>

1:19:31.458 --> 1:19:35.708
<i>-That came out meaner than I meant it to.</i>
<i>-[clears throat] No, it's all right.</i>

1:19:35.791 --> 1:19:37.500
<i>[clears throat] No, I understand.</i>

1:19:41.666 --> 1:19:42.500
<i>[Scott sighs]</i>

1:19:45.166 --> 1:19:47.416
<i>Let's just get this done. [clears throat]</i>

1:19:50.625 --> 1:19:51.708
<i>[engine starts]</i>

1:19:53.291 --> 1:19:56.666
<i>♪ Neons are a-gleaming</i>
<i>And the gamblers are a-dreaming ♪</i>

1:19:56.750 --> 1:19:58.333
<i>♪ Oh, it's night life ♪</i>

1:19:58.416 --> 1:20:00.375
<i>♪ Yeah, night life ♪</i>

1:20:00.458 --> 1:20:04.166
<i>♪ The chips go a-spilling</i>
<i>And it's time to make a killing ♪</i>

1:20:04.250 --> 1:20:05.083
<i>♪ Oh, it's night life… ♪</i>

1:20:05.166 --> 1:20:07.708
<i>Ay, su puta madre.</i> [kisses]

1:20:08.250 --> 1:20:09.083
<i>[Vanderohe] Guz!</i>

1:20:09.166 --> 1:20:11.041
<i>[zombies screeching]</i>

1:20:11.916 --> 1:20:15.875
<i>♪ The dice go a-turning</i>
<i>And you hit snake eyes ♪</i>

1:20:15.958 --> 1:20:17.875
<i>♪ You can't be a quitter… ♪</i>

1:20:17.958 --> 1:20:19.833
<i>-[growls]</i>
<i>-[screaming]</i>

1:20:23.250 --> 1:20:24.333
<i>[screeches]</i>

1:20:25.750 --> 1:20:26.625
<i>[exhales sharply]</i>

1:20:27.666 --> 1:20:30.041
<i>I got the bride. I got the bride.</i>

1:20:30.625 --> 1:20:31.958
<i>I shot her three times.</i>

1:20:32.041 --> 1:20:33.250
<i>Actually, it was four.</i>

1:20:33.333 --> 1:20:34.166
<i>Four.</i>

1:20:35.000 --> 1:20:37.375
<i>[chuckles excitedly] Whoo-hoo!</i>

1:20:38.375 --> 1:20:42.000
<i>Not zombie-killing material,</i>
<i>my ass, Mr. Vanderohe.</i>

1:20:42.083 --> 1:20:43.583
<i>[zombie shrieking]</i>

1:20:44.958 --> 1:20:46.416
<i>[Dieter] Whoo-hoo! Ha!</i>

1:20:49.125 --> 1:20:51.958
<i>Sorry, sir. Um… All right.</i>

1:20:52.750 --> 1:20:53.583
<i>Okay.</i>

1:20:58.250 --> 1:20:59.458
<i>-[beeps]</i>
<i>-[gate opens]</i>

1:21:01.291 --> 1:21:02.125
<i>[Dieter] Okay.</i>

1:21:18.500 --> 1:21:19.916
<i>Götterdämmerung.</i>

1:21:20.875 --> 1:21:23.208
<i>You've been here</i>
<i>in the dark waiting for me.</i>

1:21:24.833 --> 1:21:25.708
<i>[chuckles softly]</i>

1:21:27.041 --> 1:21:29.000
<i>You're so beautiful. See?</i>

1:21:32.291 --> 1:21:33.125
<i>Oh, look.</i>

1:21:34.250 --> 1:21:36.416
<i>There's another team of grave robbers.</i>

1:21:36.500 --> 1:21:38.166
<i>They tried to cut their way in.</i>

1:21:38.250 --> 1:21:40.583
<i>[scoffs] That's so stupid.</i>

1:21:40.666 --> 1:21:44.250
<i>You stupid poor skeletons.</i>

1:21:45.458 --> 1:21:46.875
<i>No, no, no, no, no, no, no.</i>

1:21:48.208 --> 1:21:51.750
<i>Oh, no. All they managed to do</i>
<i>is to screw up the card reader.</i>

1:21:51.833 --> 1:21:54.041
<i>[Vanderohe] Is it another team,</i>
<i>or is it us, Dieter?</i>

1:21:54.625 --> 1:21:57.250
<i>-Huh?</i>
<i>-Think about it. Us.</i>

1:22:00.333 --> 1:22:01.833
<i>I mean, look at them. It's us.</i>

1:22:02.583 --> 1:22:04.375
<i>It could be us in another timeline,</i>

1:22:04.458 --> 1:22:05.916
<i>and we're caught</i>

1:22:07.208 --> 1:22:09.541
<i>in some infinite loop</i>

1:22:09.625 --> 1:22:11.750
<i>of fighting and dying,</i>

1:22:13.291 --> 1:22:16.833
<i>fighting and dying,</i>
<i>fighting and dying. And Tanaka…</i>

1:22:20.041 --> 1:22:21.500
<i>the puppet master.</i>

1:22:21.583 --> 1:22:22.416
<i>Devil. God.</i>

1:22:23.583 --> 1:22:27.291
<i>And we, you, me, Guz,</i>
<i>and the rest of the team,</i>

1:22:27.375 --> 1:22:30.875
<i>simply pawns in some perverse play</i>

1:22:30.958 --> 1:22:33.500
<i>where we're destined</i>
<i>to repeat our failures.</i>

1:22:34.916 --> 1:22:36.041
<i>And finally,</i>

1:22:37.083 --> 1:22:40.416
<i>in some mind-bending, ironic reveal…</i>

1:22:43.666 --> 1:22:45.166
<i>it all begins again.</i>

1:22:45.916 --> 1:22:46.750
<i>Cool.</i>

1:22:47.583 --> 1:22:48.416
<i>Boom.</i>

1:22:50.916 --> 1:22:52.333
<i>[zombies screeching]</i>

1:23:11.791 --> 1:23:13.208
<i>[snarling and sniffing]</i>

1:23:14.625 --> 1:23:15.541
<i>[screeches]</i>

1:23:17.333 --> 1:23:18.208
<i>[chuckles softly]</i>

1:23:19.500 --> 1:23:20.833
<i>Amazing.</i>

1:23:21.500 --> 1:23:22.958
<i>[zombies screeching]</i>

1:23:26.500 --> 1:23:27.333
<i>There.</i>

1:23:28.791 --> 1:23:31.166
<i>That's where</i>
<i>the first pressure trigger is.</i>

1:23:31.250 --> 1:23:34.083
<i>It's some kind of a booby trap, trust me.</i>

1:23:34.791 --> 1:23:37.083
<i>If we could find something to trigger it…</i>

1:23:47.625 --> 1:23:48.958
<i>-There.</i>
<i>-I see.</i>

1:23:56.083 --> 1:23:58.333
<i>By the way, I love your hair.</i>

1:24:01.375 --> 1:24:02.208
<i>Thanks.</i>

1:24:03.375 --> 1:24:05.333
<i>[growling softly]</i>

1:24:15.500 --> 1:24:16.958
<i>[Geeta whimpering] Oh, God.</i>

1:24:17.041 --> 1:24:17.875
<i>Oh, God.</i>

1:24:20.541 --> 1:24:21.375
<i>[snarls]</i>

1:24:22.291 --> 1:24:23.125
<i>[Geeta exclaims] No!</i>

1:24:23.208 --> 1:24:24.166
<i>Oh, God.</i>

1:24:25.166 --> 1:24:26.500
<i>-[growls]</i>
<i>-[screams]</i>

1:24:27.250 --> 1:24:29.583
<i>-[growling]</i>
<i>-[all screaming]</i>

1:24:40.625 --> 1:24:41.458
<i>[growls]</i>

1:24:47.291 --> 1:24:48.166
<i>[growling softly]</i>

1:24:55.041 --> 1:24:55.958
<i>[screeching]</i>

1:24:58.166 --> 1:24:59.458
<i>[Martin] Hey, sweetheart.</i>

1:25:00.208 --> 1:25:01.041
<i>[screeching]</i>

1:25:02.416 --> 1:25:03.541
<i>[growling]</i>

1:25:07.208 --> 1:25:08.416
<i>[screeches]</i>

1:25:10.791 --> 1:25:12.416
<i>[screaming]</i>

1:25:13.500 --> 1:25:14.541
<i>Gotcha.</i>

1:25:15.291 --> 1:25:16.125
<i>[growls]</i>

1:25:17.125 --> 1:25:18.375
<i>[snarls]</i>

1:25:21.708 --> 1:25:23.208
<i>[screams]</i>

1:25:24.666 --> 1:25:26.166
<i>[growling]</i>

1:25:30.916 --> 1:25:32.375
<i>-[snarls]</i>
<i>-[grunts]</i>

1:25:33.125 --> 1:25:34.625
<i>[grunting]</i>

1:25:40.500 --> 1:25:41.500
<i>Get off me!</i>

1:25:46.666 --> 1:25:47.791
<i>[gasping]</i>

1:25:51.916 --> 1:25:54.625
<i>-You okay?</i>
<i>-Yeah. Yeah.</i>

1:25:58.041 --> 1:25:58.875
<i>Yeah.</i>

1:25:58.958 --> 1:25:59.875
<i>[zombie screeches]</i>

1:26:06.333 --> 1:26:07.916
<i>[screeching]</i>

1:26:10.291 --> 1:26:11.125
<i>Good luck.</i>

1:26:13.791 --> 1:26:14.958
<i>Hey, gorgeous.</i>

1:26:15.541 --> 1:26:17.250
<i>Hey! Whoa, whoa, whoa!</i>

1:26:17.333 --> 1:26:18.708
<i>Okay. Oh.</i>

1:26:18.791 --> 1:26:21.000
<i>Easy, easy, easy. Hey, hey, hey.</i>

1:26:22.625 --> 1:26:24.416
<i>Okay. Yeah.</i>

1:26:26.333 --> 1:26:27.416
<i>[snarling]</i>

1:26:29.375 --> 1:26:30.208
<i>[screaming]</i>

1:26:36.250 --> 1:26:37.416
<i>[growls softly]</i>

1:26:37.500 --> 1:26:39.833
<i>[sobbing] No. No.</i>

1:26:39.916 --> 1:26:42.875
<i>-[growls]</i>
<i>-No! [screams]</i>

1:26:42.958 --> 1:26:45.375
<i>-[snarling]</i>
<i>-[screaming]</i>

1:26:49.041 --> 1:26:50.083
<i>What are you doing?</i>

1:26:56.416 --> 1:26:58.958
<i>You said</i>
<i>you just needed a vial of her blood.</i>

1:26:59.541 --> 1:27:01.541
<i>[Martin] Well, forget blood.</i>

1:27:02.166 --> 1:27:06.125
<i>You know how much the whole head of</i>
<i>one of these things is worth to my boss,</i>

1:27:06.208 --> 1:27:07.333
<i>to the government?</i>

1:27:07.833 --> 1:27:08.833
<i>Mwah!</i>

1:27:09.625 --> 1:27:13.041
<i>In the right hands,</i>
<i>this is the power to make more of them.</i>

1:27:13.125 --> 1:27:15.375
<i>The power to control your own zombie army.</i>

1:27:15.458 --> 1:27:16.875
<i>That's the ultimate WMD.</i>

1:27:16.958 --> 1:27:18.500
<i>[Lilly] This isn't what we agreed to.</i>

1:27:18.583 --> 1:27:21.000
<i>Well, you want your deal or not?</i>

1:27:23.791 --> 1:27:24.625
<i>Huh?</i>

1:27:26.833 --> 1:27:27.791
<i>That's what I thought.</i>

1:27:29.833 --> 1:27:31.958
<i>So you keep your goddamn mouth shut.</i>

1:27:34.000 --> 1:27:35.041
<i>Okay, we need to go.</i>

1:27:35.125 --> 1:27:38.750
<i>Why? They gonna come looking</i>
<i>for her if she doesn't radio back to base?</i>

1:27:38.833 --> 1:27:41.083
<i>Her death cry. They'll have heard it.</i>

1:27:41.166 --> 1:27:43.291
<i>Once they find her body, our trade is off.</i>

1:27:44.958 --> 1:27:46.291
<i>What are they gonna do?</i>

1:27:47.458 --> 1:27:48.416
<i>I don't know.</i>

1:27:50.625 --> 1:27:51.833
<i>[elevator dings]</i>

1:27:56.958 --> 1:27:57.958
<i>[growling softly]</i>

1:27:59.208 --> 1:28:01.166
<i>[Guzman chuckling] Now we're talking.</i>

1:28:04.500 --> 1:28:05.666
<i>Off you go.</i>

1:28:07.625 --> 1:28:10.458
<i>Come on, go get it. That's right.</i>

1:28:11.416 --> 1:28:12.666
<i>[Guzman] Come on, fool.</i>

1:28:13.708 --> 1:28:15.333
<i>[moaning]</i>

1:28:23.875 --> 1:28:24.916
<i>[growling]</i>

1:28:25.000 --> 1:28:26.333
<i>[screaming]</i>

1:28:28.500 --> 1:28:30.000
<i>[breathing heavily]</i>

1:28:31.541 --> 1:28:32.500
<i>I… I'm okay.</i>

1:28:34.375 --> 1:28:35.833
<i>Everything's fine.</i>

1:28:39.166 --> 1:28:40.333
<i>[elevator dings]</i>

1:28:41.875 --> 1:28:43.583
<i>[Guzman] Where you getting all these?</i>

1:28:50.333 --> 1:28:51.416
<i>[microwave dings]</i>

1:28:52.250 --> 1:28:53.958
<i>-[growls]</i>
<i>-[yelps]</i>

1:28:54.041 --> 1:28:56.125
<i>Who's got the hot hand?</i>

1:28:56.708 --> 1:28:59.166
<i>All right, here we go. You can taste it.</i>

1:28:59.250 --> 1:29:01.041
<i>-[grunts softly]</i>
<i>-Huh? Huh?</i>

1:29:01.125 --> 1:29:02.666
<i>Okay, let's go get it.</i>

1:29:05.375 --> 1:29:06.208
<i>[blows]</i>

1:29:08.583 --> 1:29:09.458
<i>Watch this, Guz.</i>

1:29:15.375 --> 1:29:16.916
<i>You see that, Diet?</i>

1:29:17.000 --> 1:29:19.500
<i>-It's not the meat, it's the heat.</i>
<i>-[Dieter] Okay.</i>

1:29:20.083 --> 1:29:22.666
<i>And the deterrent should be releasing</i>

1:29:23.250 --> 1:29:25.958
<i>right… now.</i>

1:29:26.625 --> 1:29:28.333
<i>[groaning]</i>

1:29:28.416 --> 1:29:29.416
<i>[Dieter] What, that's it?</i>

1:29:29.500 --> 1:29:32.333
<i>[scoffs] Oh, wow. That's so scary.</i>

1:29:36.916 --> 1:29:37.833
<i>Oh, </i>Scheisse!

1:29:40.750 --> 1:29:41.833
<i>-[chuckles]</i>
<i>-[Dieter] Fuck.</i>

1:29:41.916 --> 1:29:44.666
<i>That was supposed to be nonlethal.</i>

1:29:44.750 --> 1:29:47.041
<i>-That has to be illegal, right?</i>
<i>-Good old Tanaka.</i>

1:29:47.125 --> 1:29:48.666
<i>Guess he wasn't screwing around.</i>

1:29:49.541 --> 1:29:51.833
<i>So is that it, Dieter, huh?</i>
<i>Is it safe now?</i>

1:29:52.416 --> 1:29:54.000
<i>I think, probably.</i>

1:29:58.375 --> 1:29:59.625
<i>[whirring]</i>

1:29:59.708 --> 1:30:00.625
<i>[growls]</i>

1:30:07.166 --> 1:30:10.333
<i>[spluttering] Okay.</i>
<i>Now, it's probably clear.</i>

1:30:12.916 --> 1:30:14.208
<i>Good luck with that.</i>

1:30:15.625 --> 1:30:18.083
<i>Oh, come on, Guz. It was just getting fun.</i>

1:30:20.125 --> 1:30:21.416
<i>[engine whirring]</i>

1:30:29.750 --> 1:30:31.000
<i>Yes.</i>

1:30:31.083 --> 1:30:33.916
<i>Yes! Yes!</i>

1:30:34.000 --> 1:30:36.166
<i>Come on! Come on!</i>

1:30:36.250 --> 1:30:38.250
<i>Yes! Yes!</i>

1:30:38.833 --> 1:30:40.833
<i>[exploding]</i>

1:30:40.916 --> 1:30:42.291
<i>[engine sputters]</i>

1:30:43.208 --> 1:30:44.375
<i>[metal clanking]</i>

1:30:47.416 --> 1:30:49.791
<i>You filthy piece of shit.</i>

1:30:50.375 --> 1:30:51.250
<i>Fuck!</i>

1:30:56.458 --> 1:30:57.791
<i>Oh, um…</i>

1:30:58.500 --> 1:30:59.916
<i>You okay there, Dieter?</i>

1:31:00.000 --> 1:31:02.083
<i>-[spluttering] I'm okay.</i>
<i>-[Vanderohe] Yeah?</i>

1:31:02.166 --> 1:31:03.208
<i>[Dieter] Um, um…</i>

1:31:03.875 --> 1:31:05.416
<i>Can you help me, Mr. Vanderohe? [gags]</i>

1:31:05.500 --> 1:31:07.041
<i>-Yeah. Absolutely.</i>
<i>-Thank you.</i>

1:31:07.125 --> 1:31:10.125
<i>One, two, three.</i>

1:31:10.208 --> 1:31:11.125
<i>[both grunting]</i>

1:31:19.000 --> 1:31:20.583
<i>[Dieter] If I can open it,</i>

1:31:21.875 --> 1:31:25.916
<i>it will be either destruction or renewal.</i>

1:31:30.416 --> 1:31:32.666
<i>Death… or rebirth.</i>

1:31:34.458 --> 1:31:35.583
<i>[snaps fingers]</i>

1:31:35.666 --> 1:31:38.916
<i>That's heavy, brother. But I dig it.</i>

1:31:39.875 --> 1:31:44.208
<i>The decision came down to the wire,</i>
<i>but ultimately, the president caved</i>

1:31:44.291 --> 1:31:47.750
<i>to the pressures to move the date</i>
<i>of the bombing off of the holiday.</i>

1:31:47.833 --> 1:31:49.833
<i>This marked a reversal</i>
<i>of his earlier position</i>

1:31:49.916 --> 1:31:52.625
<i>that dropping the nuke</i>
<i>on the Fourth would be, quote,</i>

1:31:52.708 --> 1:31:55.250
<i>"Really cool</i>
<i>and the ultimate fireworks show,"</i>

1:31:55.333 --> 1:31:59.250
<i>and quote, "Actually kind</i>
<i>of patriotic if you think about it."</i>

1:31:59.333 --> 1:32:02.000
<i>Due to fears that</i>
<i>mounting anger from humanitarian groups</i>

1:32:02.083 --> 1:32:05.208
<i>would cause the bombing</i>
<i>to be postponed indefinitely,</i>

1:32:05.291 --> 1:32:07.083
<i>the administration</i>
<i>has made the dramatic choice</i>

1:32:07.166 --> 1:32:08.750
<i>to not postpone the bombing</i>

1:32:08.833 --> 1:32:11.666
<i>but rather to move it up</i>
<i>by a full 24 hours.</i>

1:32:11.750 --> 1:32:12.666
<i>[scoffs] The fuck?</i>

1:32:12.750 --> 1:32:16.125
<i>[newscaster]</i> The scheduled drop time
now coming at sunset tonight.

1:32:16.208 --> 1:32:17.458
<i>-Stay with us…</i>
-[Martin] Mother of God.

1:32:17.541 --> 1:32:18.791
<i>[Maria] Are you fucking kidding me?</i>

1:32:18.875 --> 1:32:19.708
<i>What?</i>

1:32:19.791 --> 1:32:21.500
<i>[newscaster] </i>Keep checking back
with us here.

1:32:21.583 --> 1:32:23.041
<i>-In related news…</i>
-[Maria] It's insane.

1:32:23.125 --> 1:32:25.125
<i>…the International Society</i>
<i>of Elvis Impersonators…</i>

1:32:25.208 --> 1:32:27.125
<i>[Martin] Think that kid</i>
<i>has that safe open yet?</i>

1:32:27.208 --> 1:32:28.416
<i>[Guzman] Better get out of here.</i>

1:32:28.500 --> 1:32:29.333
<i>[metal clanking]</i>

1:32:39.250 --> 1:32:40.125
<i>[Scott] </i>Peters.

1:32:40.875 --> 1:32:41.833
<i>[Peters] </i>Yeah.

1:32:43.333 --> 1:32:44.500
<i>We got a problem.</i>

1:32:45.375 --> 1:32:46.791
<i>They moved the bomb up.</i>

1:32:46.875 --> 1:32:50.208
<i>Oh, nice. I'm glad they decided</i>
<i>to move the nuclear bomb up.</i>

1:32:50.291 --> 1:32:52.166
<i>I was getting kind of antsy.</i>

1:32:52.250 --> 1:32:54.416
<i>[Scott] </i>We've got about 90 minutes
before this place is dust.

1:32:54.500 --> 1:32:55.791
<i>How's it going up there?</i>

1:32:58.708 --> 1:33:00.208
<i>[crackling]</i>

1:33:02.083 --> 1:33:04.625
<i>Good. I actually found a pool.</i>

1:33:04.708 --> 1:33:06.625
<i>Been working on my tan.</i>

1:33:06.708 --> 1:33:09.208
<i>Gotta even this shit out.</i>
<i>You know what I'm talking about?</i>

1:33:10.166 --> 1:33:11.666
<i>How's it going over there?</i>

1:33:12.375 --> 1:33:14.208
<i>Get the safe open yet?</i>

1:33:14.291 --> 1:33:18.208
<i>It's a little slower than we thought,</i>
<i>but… we're close.</i>

1:33:18.791 --> 1:33:22.958
<i>All right. I'm just giving it</i>
<i>a wash and wax, so hurry up.</i>

1:33:23.041 --> 1:33:24.500
<i>Just waiting on you, man.</i>

1:33:24.583 --> 1:33:26.083
<i>-All set.</i>
<i>-[radio clicks off]</i>

1:33:27.375 --> 1:33:28.625
<i>Son of a bitch.</i>

1:33:29.166 --> 1:33:31.500
<i>[tense music playing]</i>

1:33:38.083 --> 1:33:39.041
<i>[elevator dings]</i>

1:33:50.291 --> 1:33:53.250
<i>-Hey, Dieter. How's that safe coming?</i>
<i>-[Dieter grunts] </i>Scheisse!

1:33:53.333 --> 1:33:54.750
<i>Scott, he's working, man.</i>

1:34:00.000 --> 1:34:02.583
<i>You see this? The four locks?</i>

1:34:02.666 --> 1:34:04.250
<i>You know what that is?</i>

